Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大英帝国的星期二\NIt's a normal Tuesday in Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,山雨欲来风满楼 漫漫车龙几时休\NThere's a hint of drizzle in the air and traffic is at a standstill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为 驾驶不该如此乏味\NWe know that driving is meant to be more fun than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,车也不该如此无聊\NWe know that cars are meant to be more fun than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们决定 帮你逃离这一切\NSo we decided what we'd do is give you an hour or so of escapism,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,给你一个小时亲近好车 亲近完美之路\Nof perfect roads and perfect cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接下来\NYeah. So, what we're going to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要将所有会产生烦恼的东西抹去\Nstrip away all the things that drive us mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,道路施工 小标致 测速探头\Nroadworks, Peugeots, speed cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-詹姆斯·梅 -对 我们不能带上他\N- James May.\N- Yeah, we'll get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他会拖我们后腿\NHe's always holding us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开始我们的完美公路之旅\NAnd then we will end up with the perfect road trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的是 杰里米坚持要从威尼斯\NStrangely, Jeremy insisted we should start here, in Venice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这个没有街道只有水道的地方出发\Nwhere all the streets are full of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要来威尼斯\NWhy are we in Venice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想驾驶这台Riva Aquarama号\NBecause I wanted to drive the Riva Aquarama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它是有史以来最曼妙的小艇\NBecause it's the most beautiful thing ever made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还拥有一对V8发动机\Nand because it's got two V8s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我们来威尼斯 是因为他想开 啥来着\NOkay, we are starting in Venice because he wanted to drive a... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Riva Aquarama号\N- Riva Aquarama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界上最美的东西\N- The most beautiful thing ever made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有 两台V8\Nand it's got... Two V8s?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,两台\N- Two V8s!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将由此出发 穿越\NAnd we're going to set off from here on a journey across Italy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,意大利 法国 直抵 哪里\Nacross France, to... Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-波城 -波城 是哪里\N- Pau. - To Pau... Pau?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要去波城\NWhy are we going to Pau?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那是第一届格兰披治大赛的举办地\NBecause that is where the first ever Grand Prix was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-波城 -没错\N- Pau? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-闻所未闻 -当年的赛道还在呢\N- Never heard of it. - The track's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将在史上首条格兰披治赛道上飞驰\NWe're going to drive the very first Grand Prix track.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 在起点和终点间 我们将途径\NWhatever. Between here and there, we're going to be on motorways,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,高速 山路 拉力赛道 场地赛道和城市\Nmountain roads, rally stages, racetracks and cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在每个点 我们都会使用\NAnd in every place, we are both going to pick what we believe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,自认为最棒的交通工具\Nis the perfect mode of transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这将会是美好的一周\NIt's going to be the perfect week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝天白云 游艇美景 万事俱备\NPerfect weather, perfect start,\Nperfect boat, perfect everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-爽 -而且詹姆斯不在\N- Perfect.\N- And no James May.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能要求 再多\NThat's better than perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的七天 我们的完美之旅\NOver the next seven days, our quest for perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,将带我们从威尼斯前往意大利湖区\Nwould take us from Venice towards the Italian Lakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后从那里往南 奔赴地中海\NFrom there we'd head south to the Mediterranean,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着法国里维埃拉沿岸 到达圣特罗佩\Nfor a drive along the French Riviera to Saint-Tropez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并再次向内陆进发 到达终点波城\NThen we'd swing inland again towards the finishing point at Pau.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不是看上去有点像美帝警探\NDo we look like Tubbs and Crockett?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}电影《迈阿密风云》中的警察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,或者天朝城管\NOr Tubby and Crotchety?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 说真的 太爽了 -天朝城管\N- No, seriously. That's perfect, though.\N- Tubby and Crotchety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大威尼斯\NVenice Vice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,靠泊好20万英镑的快艇后\NHaving docked the £200,000 speedboat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我选择了一台价格更贵的跑车\NI switched to an even more expensive car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,全新成熟版 不甩尾版 黑版 SLS\NThe new, grown-up, less tail-happy Black edition of the SLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,维多利亚时期 人们会在周游列国时\NIn Victorian times, people would come through Venice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会路过威尼斯\Non what was called "the grand tour",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我为此钦点奔驰到场\Nso that's why I've gone for the Mercedes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它是绝对的终极自驾游之王\Nbecause it is the ultimate grand tourer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它当然不是 因为你忘记了法拉利F12\NMmm-hmm. Except, it isn't the ultimate because this is, the Ferrari F12.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 那车动力太强了\NNo, no. That's too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-动力太强 -是啊\N- Too powerful?\N- It is too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前就说过\NI said that... It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是节目里说过 然后我就呵呵了\NYou did say it on the programme and I thought then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 我有能力驾驭它的全部动力\NYou see this? I will be able to use all of the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而你根本没办法榨干那台F12\NIn that, you will not be able to use all of the power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你会在半途撞上电线杆\Nbecause you'll end up halfway up a telegraph pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我绝对可以尽在掌握\NNo, I'll be able to all of the power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定还会剩余那么一点点 就是这样\Nbut there will be more power than you've got, that's all that's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一台GT必须\NA grand tourer should be powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,够快 够强 够狠\N- and creamy and grunty and... - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一台622匹马力的四轮车\NSix hundred and twenty-two horsepower,\Nit's not a wheelbarrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-730匹 比你还多 -我知道\N- Seven hundred and thirty! It's more.\N- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德\NHammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能开着GT上路了么\NLet's just go across Italy, shall we, in our grand tourers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走\NYes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会狂飙的 小样\NI'LL go quickly, you big girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欧 我的天\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,动力太凶猛了\NOh, that's a lot of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确实多了点 不 一点也不\NMaybe that's too much! No, it's not too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,杰里米个胆小鬼 动力正合适\NJeremy's being a wuss. It's just enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我目前用不了这么多\NIt's just I don't need to use all of it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要控制一些 就这么一点\NI'm going to use a bit Less. Maybe this much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,变速箱的换挡速度太惊人了\NThe changes from that gearbox are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是台双离合变速箱 其实\NIt's a double clutch gear box. In actual fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它和杰里米SLS里的那台一模一样\Nit's exactly the same unit as in Jeremy's Mercedes SLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但法拉利进行了独门调教\NIt's just Ferrari have put their own mapping,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,用法拉利的电脑控制它\Ntheir own computer control on this particular one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能在你换挡的时候\NAnd it's set up so that when you change,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它能同步匹配转速 并进行补油\Nit spikes the engine revs so it surges when you change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,阿弥陀佛\NDear God!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这台车不只是绣花枕头\NThis body isn't just pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它的设计能够最大程度地利用气流\Nit's been sculpted to maximise the air flowing over it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,产生下压力\Nto generate down force
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把车死死地摁在路上\Nto stick it to the road
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奔驰制造过好几款黑色系列\NThere have been a number of Black Special Edition Mercs in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们基本都很 无聊 真的 难以操控\Nand almost all of them have been, well, dreadful, really. Undriveable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会产生过多扭矩 每当你踩下油门\NThey generated too much torque. So every time you put your foot down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就会感觉车要自杀\Nit felt like they were trying to tear themselves apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你一路狂奔 它一路把小鸟\NYou'd be going along and it'd be sucking birds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大树 松鼠统统吸进发动机\Nand trees and squirrels into the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把蜿蜒的道路抛诸身后\Nand then ripping up the road and hurling chunks of tarmac out of the back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的非常 扯淡\Nand it was just... They were ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而在它身上 奔驰变聪明了\NThis, though, Mercedes has been clever
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 虽然它比普通版的SLS的动力更强\Nbecause, yes, it generates more power than a standard SLS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但扭矩要小14Nm 所以现在\Nbut 11 fewer torques. So now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你踩下油门 它能将你的动作转化成速度\NYou put your foot down, it translates that action into speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是事故\Nnot destructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,欧 V8简直所向披靡\NOh, but you can't beat a V8!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认 V12确实很棒 但V8更赞\NI mean, yes, a V12 is nice. But a V8 is nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么简单\NIt just is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才说V8无懈可击\NI'm just saying you can't beat a V8.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但我依然喜欢更强 更凶悍的V12\NOh, I like a 12, I do like a big powerful, slightly angry 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这车真不错\NThat's a great car, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 你轻轻戳它一下\NIt's......You just give it a little poke,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"对不起 请..."\N"Excuse me, could you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太不可思议了\NThat is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我乐翻了\NI was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可就在此时 杰里米突然调转车头\NAnd therefore a bit surprised when Jeremy suddenly veered off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来到了一个古老的意大利小镇\Ntoward some old Italian town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 就这个 -是啊\N- What? That? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是 罗密欧与朱丽叶里描写的那个阳台\NThat is the actual balcony from Romeo and Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-听我说 -干嘛\N- Yeah. Couple of points. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我开了台法拉利 晴空万里 身处意大利\NI've got a Ferrari, it's a beautiful day, I'm in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你却来围观爱情故事里的阳台\NYou're looking at a balcony that was in a story... Story!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你说过自己讨厌这个故事的作者\NMade up by a man who you said you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌莎翁 但你想...\NI hate William Shakespeare but it's...Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是假的 只是个传说 编出来的\NIt's not real, it's a story. It was pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你在畅游欧洲 要欣赏沿途名胜古迹\NYou're on a tour of Europe, you need to see stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我开着法拉利游欧洲\NI'm on a tour of Europe, in a Ferrari,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在却不在车里\Nexcept I'm not in a Ferrari,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,站在一栋破房子外面瞻仰\NI'm standing here Looking at an old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,庆幸的是 一大波TG粉围观\NHappily, a big crowd of Italian Top Gear fans then stopped him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我们放弃参观旧剧院 继续上路\Nfrom getting into some old theatre so we could get back on the motorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他接下来还停车看破房\NIf he's going to ruin this road trip
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毁我的好心情 我就...\Nby stopping off to look at old things that don't move, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我早该记得\NI should've remembered, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德是个没文化的粗人\NHammond isn't going to want to do anything cultural
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还不懂得吃货的心理\Nand he isn't going to want to eat anything interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉就像跟一个小板凳一起旅游一样\NIt's like travelling around with a garden chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我于是决定再耍他一下\NI therefore decided to annoy him some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -怎么了\N- Hammond? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能从这里出去么\NShall we turn off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 为什么\NWhat, now? Why would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我开腻了高速 想换个口味\NWell, because I'm bored of driving on motorways, I want to go on other roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,路边是不是又有一对破石头\NIs there an old pile of bricks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或者门口供着一个仙女\Nor a gate that once featured in a fairy tale down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是 只是开更有意思的路\NNo, no. It's driving but just on nice roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会去看韩塞尔与葛雷特的拎包\NWe're not going to look at Hansel and Gretel's handbag or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}韩塞尔与葛雷特是格林童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 我们正驶向意大利湖区\NIn fact, we were heading for the Italian Lakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们此次行程皇冠上的明珠\Na sparkling jewel in the golden crown of our perfect journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很快我发现 这些车和景\NAnd soon I realised that cars like these on days like these
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,之前好像也拍过 DVD意大利任务的片头\Nhave been used before, at the beginning of. The Italian job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这段路应该配什么音乐\NI know just the music we need for this bit of our drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来一首蒙罗\NCue the Monro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}迈特·蒙罗 英国著名歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些都很给力\NOoh, this is pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,开着我的意大利产超级GT 欣赏意大利美景\NLooking at all of these Italian things from my Italian grand touring supercar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们唯一需要注意的是 进隧道时\NWe just have to be careful that if we go into a tunnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要撞上推土机\Nwe don't hit a bulldozer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欧 这简直 欧\NOh, that's just... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽歪歪\NThis is just magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但很快 我发现选择这里非常明智\NBut soon the real reason for turning off became apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当道路越弯曲\NAs the roads became more twisty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,法拉利也越难以操控\Nthe Ferrari was becoming more of a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,欧\NOh-ho! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你释放那730匹马力的时候需要谨慎一些\NUh, just need to be a bit careful about unleashing 730 brake horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它比F1赛车更强劲 我必须格外小心\NIt's actually more than an F1 car and I'm conscious of that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊\NHelp! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好险\NOh! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不怕呢\NI wasn't scared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,法拉利比奔驰快这一点 我不置可否\NI have no doubt that the Ferrari is faster than this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但奔驰更适合驾驶 因为它没那么恐怖\Nbut this is just nicer to drive'cause it's less frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在F12上 法拉利提供了所有你想要的\NWith the F12, Ferrari have given you everything you need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的操控\Nto have an incredible drive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,或者给你一场严重车祸\Nor get yourself into a very great deal of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让一个赛车手来驾驶 他会说\NGet a racing driver in this car and he will tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"对 这才是一台车"\N"Yes, that is a real car."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它不是用来停在高球停车场\NIt's not been tamed for people to park at the golf course
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,或者街边酒吧\Nand talk about in the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你简直不敢相信它和普通SLS的差距\NIt's amazing how different this is to the standard SLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那车会动不动就甩尾\Nwhich would be wobbling its bottom all over everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但它不会 因为有电子差速器\NThis isn't because of its electronic differential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把它想象成保时捷GT3\NYou can think of it really like a Porsche GT3,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,更轻 更硬 更专注 为赛道而生\Nlightened, hard, focused, on it, built for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一台SLS就像是\NThe SLS behaving like this is like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾迪·伊扎德出演理查德三世\NEddie Izzard doing Richard III, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下 看一个哑剧演员扮演\NIt's almost weird to watch a pantomime character
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,心直口快 聪明伶俐的角色\Nbecome so straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,诡异但不失智慧\NWeird and yet brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最后 我们来到了旅店\NEventually, we reached our overnight halt
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和我低调奢华有内涵的同事共进晚餐\Nand I went for supper with my cultured colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么说自己喜欢湖区\NWhat do you mean you prefer the Lake District?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里美得没边\NWell, this is beautiful It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-而且我觉得... -比德文特湖还漂亮\N- And to be honest, for me...\N- More beautiful than Derwentwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,加尔达湖都望尘莫及\NGarda's not even the prettiest lake and look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它太迷人 把镜头缩小到整个画面的75%\NIt's very lovely. Just scale it down to 75% of that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后配上些雨水\Nand then introduce a bit of drizzle and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keswick在湖区么 -当然\N- Is Keswick in the Lake District? - Ooh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但你在Keswick可吃不到这些 尝过没\NWhat you don't get in Keswick are these. Have you had one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-没 -吃个辣椒 来\N- No. - Have a pepper. Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 尝尝 你会喜欢的\NEat. Eat it. Go on, you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真难吃\NI don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,后来 我们决定玩个老的游戏\NThen we thought we'd play our favourite game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他手里有一张法拉利的选配表\NHe's got the Ferrari options pricelist there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我来猜配件的报价\Nand I'm going to guess how much they cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这纸上有好多好多选装件\NThere are quite a Lot of options available.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,比如\NPick some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 碳纤维赛车座椅\NOkay. Racing seats with carbon fibre.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 600镑\NI don't know, 600 quid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,5148镑\N£5,184.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-我猜的有点低 -是啊\N- I was a bit under. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,轮胎上的碳纤维轮毂盖 就是 你懂的\NBut carbon fibre wheel caps, on the tyres, you know, on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-那个防尘盖 -对\N- What, dust caps? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-碳纤维防尘盖 几个钱\NCarbon fibre dust caps? Tenner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,480镑 挺便宜的\N£480. I thought that was cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-只是四个防尘盖 -是啊\N- What, for four dust caps? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要480镑\N£480?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,杯架是不是标配\NAre the cup holders standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以买一个碳纤维杯架\NThere is a carbon fibre cup holder you can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-杯架也碳纤维 -对啊 就是插杯子的地方\N- A carbon fibre cup holder? - Yeah, you know, it pops in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候兰博基尼盖拉多的卖600镑\NWell, they were £600 on a Lamborghini Gallardo a while back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我猜一千左右\Nso I'LL go a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,2112镑 你看 吓死你\N£2,112. Yeah, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 车本身算是最便宜的选择了\NReally, the car is the cheapest option.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天 我们查了一下地图发现\NThe next day, we consulted a map and realised
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自己差点赶上了F1赛历中最高速的比赛\Nwe were just a spit from the fastest Grand Prix track on the calendar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,蒙扎\NMonza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,速度圣殿\NThe Cathedral of Speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它的高速\NBecause it's so fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,迫使我丢下了法拉利 鸟枪换炮\NI've ditched the Ferrari and upped the ante
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,找来了帕加尼Huayra\Nto this Pagani Huayra,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也有一台V12 但加了两颗涡轮\Nstill a V12 but now with two turbos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 你需要的是一颗导弹\NCause what you need here is a missile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我选择了保时捷Cayman S\NI've gone for a Porsche Cayman S.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-你疯了 -没有\N- You're just being obtuse. - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定疯了 搞了一台保时捷\NYou are. You've gone for a Porsche
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,却不是911 太气人了\Nso you can not go for a 911. It's just annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它明显比911更厉害\NThis is better than a 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么可能 当然911更快 -当然不是\N- It isn't! A 911 is better than that. - It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-911的发动机在这里 -是的\N- Because the 911 has its engine here. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-但它是中置 -因为它不是911\N- This is mid-engine. - Because it isn't a 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-不对 -它更好\N- No! - It's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 如果我们在Cadwell公园或Lydden山\NListen, if we were driving around Cadwell Park, Lydden Hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-然后 -道路蜿蜒曲折 没错\N- Yeah. - Nippy and fizzy, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是在蒙扎 你需要动力\NBut not here at Monza. You need power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是冲着这条\NYou're just hung up on this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-直得不能再直的直路来的 -当然\N- great big long straight. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但那后面一定会出现一个弯角\NBut there must be a corner down there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,否则你不可能从那里绕回来\Notherwise you wouldn't be able to get down there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且至少有两个弯角\NThere has to be......In fact there've got to be two corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错 至少有两个 -对\N- Yes, genius, that's two corners. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有你的 但你可否知道\NBrilliant. Do you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,帕加尼Huayra过弯能力非常非常强\NThe Pagani Huayra goes around corners really incredibly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定不敢相信它的攻弯速度\NYou will not believe how fast this goes around corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok -灰常灰常牛逼\N- Okay. - It's a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实不喜欢保时捷\NIt's true, I don't like Porches
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也不喜欢开保时捷的人\Nand I don't much like the people who drive them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是那两个叫詹姆斯和理查德的\Nespecially the ones called James and Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢老款的Cayman\NI didn't much like the original Cayman, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我称之为保时鸡\NI called it the Cockster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这台车也有一些不讨我喜欢的地方\NAnd there are one or two things that I don't much like about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,比如外形 我觉得它看上去太像911\NThe styling, for example, I think it looks too like a 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有座椅 肩部空间太窄\NAnd then there's the seats, the shoulder bolsters are too narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你像我一样膀大腰圆\NSo, if you're broad-shouldered and hunky, like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,会一直感觉空间狭小\Nyou're getting sort of squashed all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但剩下的一切绝对顶尖\NHowever, the rest of it is absolutely sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,配上自适应悬架 整个驾乘\NYou've got these adaptive dampers, which means that it rides
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,操控 转向 都非常接近超级跑车\Nand handles and steers like the very best supercars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但最棒的还是3.4升水平对置六缸发动机\NBut the best thing is the engine. A 3.4-litre flat six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不会出现任何差错\NThere's just no thing about it that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且每时每刻 你都能听到\NAnd all the time it makes this... You can hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,深沉 喜人的声音\Ndeep, reassuring noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,像是把理查德·伯顿塞进了机舱里\Nit's like having Richard Burton in the boot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}理查德·伯顿 英国著名演员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,无休止地抱怨你的发型\Nendlessly complimenting you on your hair
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着 和驾驶风格\Nand your clothes and your driving style.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 它太快了\NOh, my God! That is so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我去\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,230, 240, 250,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,每小时260公里\N260 kilometres an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,270 妈呀\N270! Oh, dear God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,简直吓尿了\NOh! I scared the crap out of myself then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我勒个...\NHoly sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽了\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,神车一台\NWhat a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,蒙扎就是速度的象征\NMonza is all about speed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而帕加尼Huayra则为风代言\Nand a Pagani Huayra is about that and very little else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,6.3升 V12 双涡轮\N6.3-litre, v12, twin turbos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,超级强劲的动力\NTruly, enormously powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,转向时宽胎产生巨大的抓地力\NTurning in, immense grip from those fat tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有主动空气动力学 帮我紧贴赛道\NI have aero, active aero keeping me planted on the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这些翼片都有着自己的作用\NThese things are built to work as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是单纯的装饰品\Nthey're not some fragile trailer queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我驾驶的这台车跑了86,000公里\NThis car I'm in has done 86,000 kilometres.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我猜 这车可不是一般人能对付的\NAnd I'm guessing not many of them were gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,法拉利也许同样优秀 但还是不及Huayra\NThe Ferrari would've been good at this but not as good as the Huayra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于 哈蒙德快过头了\NThe problem is Hammond is going too fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没机会品味这条史诗般荣耀的赛道\Nhe's not savouring this glorious, historical tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他只能走马观花 狼吞虎咽\NHe's just wolfing it down, like a dog wolfs down a steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而我在做的则是细细咀嚼 享受着每一口\NWhat I'm doing is masticating,\Nenjoying every mouthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米开着错误的车在赛道上爬来爬去的时候\NHAMMOND: As Jeremy crawled\Nround in his wrong car,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等着他回P房\NI was waiting for him\Nto get back to the pits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他要有好一会才能回来 是吧\NHe's going to be a while, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他不在 来看看帕加尼的内饰\NWhile he's gone, let me show you\Nthe interior of the Pagani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝对值得一看\NIt's worth seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,设计师们想让内饰很特别 我觉得他们做到了\NThey want it to feel special in here\Nand I think they've succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的确为此动了脑筋\NThey've really put thought into this,\Nmaking it feel special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,换档杆这里 所有的这些部分\NThis gear linkage here,\Nall these parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,总共有67个组成零件\Nthere's 67 components have gone\Ninto making that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因而你能看见它是怎样工作的\Nin that skeleton form,\Nso you can see it working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而用料方面也很实在\NAnd the materials, too,\Nit's all genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,用了一大堆碳纤维 真皮 和铝制品\Na lot of real carbon fibre,\Nreal leather. And the aluminium,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼前的每一个铝制部件都不是铸造的\Nevery single aluminium component\Nyou can see in here isn't cast,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而是用一整块毛坯打磨而来\Nit's milled from a single piece,\Na single billet, a lump of aluminium.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都让人感觉它值这个价\NAll of which means it feels\Nas expensive as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这车 那家伙还没回来呢吧\NI like this car.\NHe's not back yet, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是世界上唯一拥有两个lesbos弯的赛道\N第一个很窄\NThis is the only track in the world with\Ntwo lesbos, the first one's quite tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而第二个 你可以尽情把车尾甩出\Nsecond one, though,\Nyou can really hang your arse out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,总共十二个气缸 咱们来数一数好消磨时光\NIt's 12 cylinders in total.\NLet's count them, it'll pass the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 我数的有点快了 不妨慢一点\NOne, two... Oh, I'm going too quickly,\Nmight as well make it last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,三 哦等等\NThree... Oh, hang on. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在一定觉得\NYou must be feeling now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啥 你选错车了\N- What?\N- ...that you brought the wrong car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我给你读点关于这车的评价\NLet me read you something, if I may.\NTalking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这辆车在弯道里的平衡性接近完美\N"The car's cornering balance\Nis near perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,油门的预见性很中立而且正确\N"neutral but unerringly predictable\Non a balanced throttle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它会稍稍转向不足\N"and biased ever so slightly\Ntowards understeer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,若你是在前轮横向负载减轻前\N"if you throttle up\Nbefore you begin easing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大脚给油的话\N"the lateral load\Nout of the front tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我说的 是Autocar杂志上写的\NNot my words, the words of\NAutocar magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哇偶 可这到底什么意思啊\NWow! What do those words actually mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道 -我也是\N-I've no idea.\N-Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我要再去跑跑\NBut I'm going to go back\Nout there now and throttle up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在出弯前猛然加速 看会发生什么\Nbefore I've eased the lateral load out\Nof the front tyres and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我这就去\N- Yeah!\N- That's what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不懂那都啥意思\NI have no idea what any of that means.\NI haven't a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 大脚油\NRight! Throttle up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 看见了没\NOh, now you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只是打个转而已\NNow, that's just a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了没 Autocar 这明明是转向过度\NNow, you see, Autocar, that's oversteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候你读路试的文章会想 你丫到底在说啥\NSometime you read road tests and you\Ndo think, "What are you on about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是辆好车啊 你可以尽情的甩屁股\NIt's a really nice car\Nand you can get the arse out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,终于回来了\NHAMMOND: Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还装作玩得很开心吗 是的\N-Still pretending to have fun?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-额 屎粑粑会跟这差不多吗 -什么\N- Will, uh, will Poo be like this?- Will what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,屎粑粑 当我们到那儿的时候\NPoo, when we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦你是说Pau啊\NOh, Pau?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我最喜欢哪一段吗\NDo you know my favourite bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,恩恩\N你可以\N- HAMMOND: Yes. Yes.\N- You could...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,保时捷能像一条闪电一样划过那里\NThe Porsche through there,\Nit's just a streak of lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有车能比它更快\NNothing is faster than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有车可以 那个弯也是\NNothing is.\NNothing's faster... Or through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你丫有点忘乎所以了吧 这辆小车是挺快\NYes, you're getting a bit carried away.\NIt's fast. It's a quick little car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话它在这块跑更合适点\NTo be honest,\Nit's more at home in this bit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你能从商店门口飞奔过去\NYou could "Oh, look!" past the shops
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然后喊 那有个学校还有个超市\Nand "Oh, there's a school\Nand a supermarket."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是你的车该出现的地方 不是这里\NAnd that's really where it belongs.\NNot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了 我没错\N- You're wrong.\N- I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德我可以跟你赌任何东西 保时捷在这开得更快\NHammond, I bet you anything you like\Nthat around here the Porsche is faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米这也太\NJeremy, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧\N输的人要这样说\N- Okay!\N- Whoever loses has to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱詹姆斯梅\N"I love James May."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要对着镜头说\NThey have to say that\Non television to a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会是你对着镜头说 我爱詹姆斯梅的\NYou actually have to go up to the camera\Nand go, "I love James May."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊我倒希望看着你这么说\NAll right. Well, I look forward\Nto hearing you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦这原来叫lesmos\NOh, they're lesmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这里是lesbo 其实是lesmo\NI thought there was lesbo one and...\NIt's lesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin Brundle念的时候一定是感冒了\NMartin Brundle must have had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,走你\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,3 2 1 出发(意大利语）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,出发\NAnd we are away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪这简直太尴尬了\NOh, God! This is just embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样虐他连点成就感都没有\Nbecause where's going to be my sense of\Nachievement when I thrash him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对车来说有个问题\NCLARKSON: There is a point with cars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当他们变得马力很强 跑得很快的时候\Nwhere they become\Nso powerful and so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也会很疯狂很吓人\Nthey become too hectic\Nand too frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是怀亚所存在的问题\NThat's the problem with the...\N Huayra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,正在过第一个lesmo弯\NThrough the first of the lesmo corners,\Nas it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这听起来很二\NCLARKSON: I know it sounds silly\Nbut once you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当你开一辆五百多匹的车时 你反而会更慢\Nbeyond 500-550 horsepower,\Nyou end up driving the car more slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪不过真的是这样的\NIt's weird but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,用拎着刀去跟枪斗来形容这场比赛\NNever has there beem\Na more stark example of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真是再合适不过了\Nbringing a knife to a gunfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而开保时捷 我在任何地方都可以全油门\NThe Porsche, around here,\NI'm absolutely pinning it everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这难不倒我 一点也不吓人 简单得很\NIt doesn't worry me,\Nit's not frightening, it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而那辆车\NThat thing, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会见证的\NWell, we shall see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的会被证实 他则会说 我爱詹姆斯梅\NMy case will be proven and he will be\Nsaying, "I love James May."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了那里显示着270KM/H\NThat's 270 I saw there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.64,0:24:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会看到这个数字的\NHe won't see anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了一个小矮人正在接近\NI hear the sound of\Nan approaching midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,马力全开\NFully on the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,准备\NReady, steady...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,冲线啦\NAnd across the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,2分14秒8\NTwo minutes, 14.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称之为2分15\NWe'll call it 2:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来轮到卡门了\NThen it was the Cayman's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.88,0:24:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,意大利语\N(SPEAKING ITALIAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.68,0:24:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 这样比一点意思都没有\NReally, I am taking no pleasure in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.68,0:24:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他需要好好地上一课\NBut he does need to learn a lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.24,0:24:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能仅仅因为你喜欢这辆车\Nthat you can't just go making\Nstupid claims about a car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.72,0:24:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就大放厥词\Njust 'cause you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 那玩意儿的圈速\N我甚至可以用煮蛋计时器来测\NNo, seriously, that thing round...\NI could be using an egg timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.28,0:25:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他难道觉得能靠技术把时间补回来\NHow does he imagine he can\Npossibly make up enough time?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,无论他觉得自己有多厉害\NNo matter how good\Nhe thinks he is in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显 绝对不会赢的 管他呢\NClearly, it's not going to... Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.08,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说啥呢\N老大\N- You what?\N- Mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你你你怎么不\NWhere... Why aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.52,0:25:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说是我开啊\NI didn't say I'd be driving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.36,0:25:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我靠 那是谁\NWell, who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.48,0:25:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有人说是试替哥 确实是他\NWell, some say it's The Stig, and it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.84,0:25:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你有说过必须是我开吗 没说过\NDid you at any point say\NI had to drive it? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.00,0:25:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你有说过你要用试替哥吗\NDid you at any point say\Nyou were going to use The Stig?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.28,0:25:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你为啥不用呢\NWhy would you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.92,0:25:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我认为 在每条定义\NBecause I think\Nin every possible definition,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,每项规则里 这都算作弊\Nin every set of rules, it's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.80,0:25:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他回来了\NOh, here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.00,0:25:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,2分13秒2\NHAMMOND: 2:13:2.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.80,0:25:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,2分13秒2\N是的\N- 2:13:2.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.08,0:25:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑了2分14秒8 差了一秒\NYou were 2:14:8. So he's one point...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.20,0:25:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来 女士们先生们 保时捷正如我所说\NSo, there you are, ladies and gentlemen,\Nthe Porsche is, as I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.28,0:26:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,比怀亚更快\Nfaster than the, uh...\N Huayra.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它才是更明智的选择\NAnd therefore was a more\Nsensible choice of car.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.76,0:26:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-不不不 是试替哥比我快 -咋了\N- No. The Stig is faster than me.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.32,0:26:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而试替哥比谁都快 这是他存在的意义\NBut The Stig is faster than everyone,\Nthat's the point of The Stig,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.24,0:26:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,否则他会炸掉的\Nif he wasn't he'd explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.72,0:26:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开着奔驰和法拉利离开蒙扎的时候\NCLARKSON: As we left Monza\Nin the Mercedes and the Ferrari,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.96,0:26:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛有点阴沉\Nthe mood was glum.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.80,0:26:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是作弊\NIt's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.68,0:26:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,然而第二天早上看到过夜的小镇的名字时\NCLARKSON: The next morning, however,\NHammond cheered up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.84,0:26:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德就开心起来了\Nwhen he discovered the name of the town\Nwhere we'd stayed the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.84,0:26:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,从胸罩镇前往法国的路上\NFrom Bra to the French Riviera,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.88,0:26:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本可以走高速公路\Nwe could've used the motorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.76,0:26:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们决定要改走一条\NBut we decided instead
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.48,0:26:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最美妙的\Nto use the finest switchback roads
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.16,0:26:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,曲折的小路\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.84,0:26:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着要扔掉奔驰\NThis meant ditching the Mercedes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.40,0:26:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和法拉利\Nand the Ferrari
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.68,0:26:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而选这两个小家伙来代替\Nand opting for these instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.56,0:27:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样子的路上\NOn a road like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.32,0:27:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要一辆小车 一辆掀背小钢炮\Nyou need something small,\Nyou need a hot hatchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.88,0:27:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要一辆掀背小钢炮的话\NAnd if you're going to get\Na hot hatchback,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.84,0:27:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不选钢炮之王 就这辆\Nwhy not get the king? This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.72,0:27:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,高尔夫GTI\NThe Golf GTI.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很爱第1代\NI loved the Mk1
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.24,0:27:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,16气门的第2代也不赖\Nand the 16-valve Mk2 wasn't bad, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.24,0:27:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是后来的版本 它们虽然也不错\NBut since then...\NI mean, they weren't bad
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.72,0:27:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是仿佛失去了魔力一般\Nbut the magic went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.12,0:27:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而在这辆第七代上 魔力又回来了\NWith this one, though, the Mk7,\Nit is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.04,0:27:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这辆车是全能型的\NThis car can do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.00,0:27:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,装配质量不错 价格合理\NIt's well made, it's sensibly priced.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很经济环保 配置也不错\NIt's economical, it's well-equipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.08,0:27:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,能坐五个人 有个大后备箱\NIt seats five, it's got a big boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是抛开这些不谈\NBut strip all that away and underneath,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.24,0:27:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,本质上它就是一辆小钢炮\Nits DNA is hot hatchery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.24,0:28:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,2升涡轮增压引擎 220匹\NTwo-litre turbo engine, 220 horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.88,0:28:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何扭矩转向\Nand no torque steer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.48,0:28:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧着 大脚油过这个发卡弯\NNow, watch this. Foot hard down,\Ngoing around a hairpin bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.84,0:28:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太让人惊讶了\NIt's just astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.76,0:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这车的前差速器好的让人难以置信\NThe front diff on this is beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哇偶 天哪太棒了\NWhoa! God, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他又选错车了\NHe's got it wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.00,0:28:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,高尔夫GTI 确实不错\NThe Golf GTI, it's a brilliant car,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.84,0:28:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它或许是最好的全能型车\Nit's probably the best all-rounder\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 重点就在这\NBut that's... That's the point,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.64,0:28:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要全能型车\Nan all-rounder is exactly\Nwhat you don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.32,0:28:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全能不可避免的意味着要处处妥协\NAn all-rounder\Nis inevitably compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.00,0:28:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要掀背钢炮的本质\NI just want pure distilled\Nessence of hot hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.24,0:28:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就只有一个选择了\NAnd that means only one thing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.72,0:28:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉年华ST\NThe Fiesta ST.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当福特设计这辆车的时候 他们只是把零件拼到一起\NWhen Ford put this car together,\Nthey assembled all the right bits
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.00,0:29:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后想 恩 我估计这样挺好\Nand thought, "Yeah, I reckon\Nthat would be good."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.68,0:29:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们恐怕估计不到\NI don't think they could\Npossibly have known
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.76,0:29:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这车到底有多好\Nquite how good\Nit was going to turn out to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.04,0:29:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这车太出乎人意料了\Nbecause it's astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这车的确不如高尔夫马力大\NIt's down on power\Ncompared to the Golf, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.20,0:29:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是它更小 更钢炮\NBut it's smaller, that's more hot hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.80,0:29:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,更轻\NAnd it's lighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.00,0:29:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,意味着马力重量比基本上和高尔夫一样了\Nwhich means the power-to-weight ratio\Nis pretty much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.28,0:29:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,另外这辆车还敏捷的很\NAnd it's beyond nimble.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.44,0:29:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,过弯时如果随意一点的话\NYou start to just take\Nliberties with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.96,0:29:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,走线故意放宽一点\NDeliberately running a line\Na little bit wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.32,0:29:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能享受把它拉回来的乐趣了\Nso you get the pleasure\Nof turning it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.28,0:29:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太美妙了\NIt's superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.00,0:29:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界上最棒的开心方向盘\NIt's the biggest grin-maker\NI think the world has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.88,0:29:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到达下一个村子的时候 不可避免的\NIn the next village, though, inevitably
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.72,0:29:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米决定我们应该吃点什么\NJeremy decided we should\Nget something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.80,0:29:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你咋不吃饭呢\NWhy aren't you eating your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.08,0:29:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢意面\NI don't like pesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.28,0:29:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 我不喜欢吃意面\N- What?\N- I don't like pesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.44,0:30:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥不喜欢 就是不喜欢\N- Why not?\N- It's just bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.76,0:30:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还有另一个停下来的理由\NCLARKSON: There was, however,\Na very good reason why we'd stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.24,0:30:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你得说出来 你打赌输了 必须说出来\NYou've got to say it.\NYou lost the bet, you've got to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.88,0:30:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不说\NI'm not saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.04,0:30:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须说\NYou've got to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我正大光明的打败了你 保时捷就是更快\NI beat you fair and square.\NThe Porsche was faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.64,0:30:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-一点也不公平 你丫作弊 -快说\N- It wasn't fair. You cheated.\N- Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.08,0:30:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啥\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.04,0:30:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,James May\N...James May.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.64,0:30:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样行了吧 -不 要说清楚\N-There.\N-No. Say it so it's audible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.12,0:30:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱James May\NI... love James May.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.24,0:30:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这事办妥了以后我们又上路了\NCLARKSON: With that done,\Nwe got back in our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.56,0:30:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当提到美国公路旅行的时候你会想到\N纪念碑谷地\NWhen you think of an American road trip,\Nyou think of Monument Valley,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.84,0:30:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那条路笔直通向远方\Nthat road spearing off\Ninto the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.72,0:30:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这条路就相当于欧洲的纪念碑谷\NWell, this is Europe's equivalent\Nof Monument Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是目前这趟旅途中我最喜欢的一段了\NThis might just be my favourite bit\Nof our trip so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好车配美景\NThe car, the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.64,0:30:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎一个完美了得\NThis is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.20,0:31:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝创造这边地方的目的\NWhen God was making\Nthis part of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.20,0:31:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了小钢炮\N这条路就是为小钢炮量身定制的\Nit was for hot hatchbacks.\NThat's what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.48,0:31:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然而很不幸\NUnfortunately, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.08,0:31:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们激情的下山之旅被迫停止\Nour headlong charge down the Alps
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.56,0:31:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们已经无路可走\Nwas halted because we ran out of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.92,0:31:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯 -啥\N- Mmm, that.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.28,0:31:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是传说中的蒙地卡罗\N如果在那里开着大众和福特\NWell, it's Monte-Carlo.\NIf we drive into there
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.72,0:31:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会被当作流浪汉被抓起来\Nin a Volkswagen and a Ford,\Nthey'll arrest us for vagrancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.36,0:31:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理哦\NThat's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.48,0:31:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-你可以是个军火贩子 -是\N- I mean, you can be an arms dealer...\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.88,0:31:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能开着一辆嘉年华在里面转悠\N...but you can't drive around\Nin a Fiesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.36,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是底线 -我们得换车了\N- There's a limit.\N- We're going to need to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.84,0:32:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们为了显摆而换的车\NFor posing,\Nthese were the cars we selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.88,0:32:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德的兰博基尼 Aventador Roadster\NA Lamborghini Aventador Roadster\Nfor Hammond
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和我的布加迪威龙\Nand a Bugatti Veyron for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.52,0:32:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是一般的威龙\NNow, this is no ordinary Veyron,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.12,0:32:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是 Grand Sport Vitesse 版本的\Nthis is the Grand Sport Vitesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.40,0:32:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,8升 4凸轮轴 W16发动机\NEight-litre, quad-cam W16.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.60,0:32:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,极速404km/h\NTop speed 251 miles an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.12,0:32:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没车顶的\Nwith no roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.12,0:32:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是这车该待的地方\NHere it is in its natural habitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.64,0:32:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是2档\N出发后第一次\NI'm in second gear.\NI'm now using second gear
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.84,0:32:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上2档\Nfor, well, the first time\Nsince I set off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.24,0:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,又回到1档了\NAnd back down to first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.72,0:32:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇妙的一点是这里的人们在十点钟\NIt is extraordinary that here men get up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.60,0:32:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,从单身公寓中醒来\Nfrom their bachelor pads at about 10:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.00,0:32:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开着用逃税的钱买的车\Nget into their cars that they bought\Nusing money they should have paid in tax
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.80,0:32:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,花上一整天的时间\Nand then spend all day
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.72,0:33:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里一圈一圈地转\Ndriving round and round\Nand round in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.56,0:33:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以理解\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.76,0:33:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,人们看着我开着橙色的兰博基尼 Aventador Roadster\NPeople see me in my orange\NLamborghini Aventador Roadster
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.80,0:33:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得我肯定是个有钱有势的土豪\Nand think, "Yes.\NThere's a man of potency and wealth."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.04,0:33:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是两秒钟之后\N当他们看到那辆布加迪\NAnd then two seconds later,\Nthey see that Bugatti Veyron
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.00,0:33:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们肯定会想 来了一个更大的土豪\Nand think, "There's a richer,\Nmore powerful man."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.36,0:33:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计很抱歉\NI'm sorry about this, mate,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.44,0:33:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你又一次选错车了\Nbut once again,\Nyou're in the wrong car.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.24,0:33:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我对 再一次 表示异议\NI take issue with the "once again"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.84,0:33:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过 这是有史以来第一次 我选错了车\Nbut, yes, for the first time,\NI've got the wrong car.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.40,0:33:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,压根没人在看你 一个都没有\NNobody is looking at you,\Nnobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我花了29万英镑买了辆兰博基尼\NIf I had spent 290,000
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在摩纳哥里面开\Non a Lamborghini to drive around Monaco
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.12,0:33:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却开着那玩意\Nand you turned up in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.68,0:33:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨不得开车撞墙\NI'd just drive this into a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.28,0:33:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界上最势利的地方了\NThis is the snobbiest place on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.28,0:33:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里使\NIt makes...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.28,0:33:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这里让洛杉矶看上去如同朝鲜\NIt makes Los Angeles\Nlook like North Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.36,0:33:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当你要让别人代客泊车的时候\NAnd this snobbery is an issue
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.04,0:33:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这种势利就变成了个问题\Nwhen you try to\Nget your car valet parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.60,0:34:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的问题是\N这哥们开着最便宜的法拉利\NThe problem is that chap has just\Nturned up outside the Hotel de Paris
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.68,0:34:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,加利福尼亚\Nin a Ferrari California.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.68,0:34:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来到巴黎大饭店门口\NThe cheapest Ferrari there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.16,0:34:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 他依然很喜欢他的车\NNevertheless, he likes it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.64,0:34:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 这车确实不错\N所以它就停在酒店门口了\NYeah, and it's nice.\NAnd as a result, it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.16,0:34:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-就因为这是辆好车 -是的\N- Okay? 'Cause it looks good.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.52,0:34:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一分钟内\NBut in a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.84,0:34:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一个哈萨克斯坦的军火贩子\N就会开着一辆更好的车停到这里\Na Kazakhstani arms dealer\Nis going to arrive in a nicer car
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.76,0:34:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这辆法拉利就会被开走\Nand the Ferrari\Nis going to be taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.24,0:34:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被停到城市另一头的立体停车场里\Nand put in a multi-storey\Non the other side of Monaco.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.96,0:34:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们\NHAMMOND: But we pull up there
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.04,0:34:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,开着布加迪威龙和Aventador\Nin a Bugatti Veyron and\Na Lamborghini Aventador Roadster,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.40,0:34:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说会有比这俩还牛的车出现\Nare you're saying something better\Nis going to come along than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.36,0:34:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证在蒙地卡罗\NIn Monte-Carlo, I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.80,0:34:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有人会开着企业号飞船出现\Nsomeone would turn up\Nin the USS Enterprise
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.80,0:34:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们的车就会被扔进立体停车场\Nand our cars would be\Nin the multi-storey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.12,0:34:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,车有多好一点也不重要\NIt doesn't matter how good your car is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.16,0:34:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,停车员总会把车开走的\Nthe valet parkers will ultimately\Ntake it away
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.00,0:34:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没有最好只有更好\Nbecause something better always arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.04,0:34:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会有解决方案的\N这是一次完美的公路旅行\NThere's got to be a way around this.\NThis is the perfect motoring trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.52,0:35:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们的目标是\N在这次完美公路之旅中\NSo we go and check in there, in a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.80,0:35:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-开着一辆车到这酒店并入住 -嗯\N- on our perfect road trip...\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.60,0:35:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要求我们第二天早上出来的时候\N车还停在原地不动\N...we come out in the morning,\Nit's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.24,0:35:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的挑战\NThat's our challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.32,0:35:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会相当特别\NIt's going to have to be pretty special.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.92,0:35:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦耶\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.28,0:35:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然而哈蒙德却选择了\NHammond, however, opted to go
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.96,0:35:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上销量最好的车型之一\Nwith one of the best-selling cars\Nthe world has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.56,0:35:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,福特T型车\NA Model T Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.64,0:35:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但却有个棘手的问题\NAnd straightaway there was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.00,0:35:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会开这辆车\NWe didn't know how it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.56,0:35:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好 等一下\NRight, now, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.72,0:35:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们把东西理清楚\NLet's list the things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.00,0:35:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这有三个踏板\NThere are... There's three pedals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.40,0:35:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么 换挡杆在哪 这是换挡杆吗\NHow do you... Where's the gear?\NIs this the gear? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.56,0:35:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 如果 我踩的这个不是离合器\NHAMMOND: Oh, if it's......\NI haven't got my foot on the clutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.64,0:35:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-那不是离合器-好吧\N- That isn't the clutch.\N- Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.44,0:35:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个是油门\NWhich one's the accelerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.80,0:35:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是油门\N我们确定油门不是在踏板上\NThat's the accelerator.\NIt isn't a pedal, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.56,0:35:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这我怎么踩得到\NHow am I going to get my foot up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.68,0:35:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,额 那是干啥的\N好吧 让我们来启动发动机\N- Um... What's that do?\N- Right, well, start it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.16,0:35:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这才不是启动按钮呢\N- That's not the starter!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.44,0:35:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,最终哈蒙德成功发动了\NEventually,\NHammond did make it begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.32,0:35:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那时我们才发现他不知道如何刹车\NBut then we learned\Nhe didn't know how to make it stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.00,0:35:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这个是干啥的\NOh, now what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.84,0:35:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们越开越快了\NWe're going faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.04,0:36:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是手刹\N快停下\NThat's not the handbrake.\NStop it. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下来\N- Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.20,0:36:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.96,0:36:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 向前开\NRight, forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.28,0:36:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-等等 准备好了 -向前开\N- Hang on. Now, ready.\N- Forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.44,0:36:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-这可不是向前啊 -完全不是\N- That's not forwards.\N- No, it's not at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.24,0:36:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下了\NStop it. Make it stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.72,0:36:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你造吗 这车一点也不想停下来\NIt doesn't really want to, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.96,0:36:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下\NMake it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,额 杰里米 我们阻碍了整个摩纳哥的交通\NUh, Jeremy, we've held up Monaco.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.12,0:36:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗 -你自己看\N- Have we?\N- Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.60,0:36:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,额滴神啊\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.56,0:36:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然而很快我就接近目的地了\NSoon, however,\Nwe were nearing our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.32,0:36:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德啊 我一般很少这样说\NIt's not often I say this, Hammond,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.20,0:36:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但你真是太天才了\Nbut you have been a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.88,0:36:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没这样夸过我\NYou have never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.04,0:36:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果我们都不会开这个车\NBecause if we can't drive this,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.32,0:36:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎大饭店的停车员\N又有多大几率能开走这车呢\Nwhat chance do the valet parkers\Nat the Hotel de Paris have?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.52,0:36:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能开走\N这是我干过最难的事情了\NNone, it's the hardest thing\NI've ever done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.52,0:36:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会想移走这辆车却无能为力\NThey'll want to move this\Nbut they won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.88,0:36:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.52,0:36:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 先生\N- Bonjour, monsieur.\N- Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,熄火\NShut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.12,0:36:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,交给你了\NAll yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N- Bonjour.\N- Bonjour.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.12,0:36:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NBonjour.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.44,0:37:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么停车员们能成功吗\NSo, would the valet staff\Nbe successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.68,0:37:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.28,0:37:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然他们失败了\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.84,0:37:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,论如何打败专职停车员\NSo, there we go.\NThat is how to beat the valet parkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.24,0:37:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,买一辆他们不会开的车\NBuy a car they can't drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.96,0:37:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是问题是\NYes, but the problem is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们要驾车\Ntoday we are going
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.44,0:37:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,从蔚蓝海岸到Saint-Tropez\Ndown the French Riviera to Saint-Tropez
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.00,0:37:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想\Nand I'm not sure
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.28,0:37:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,开着这车去那里\NI want to go in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.88,0:37:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我到哪也不想开这车\NI'm not sure\NI'd actually go anywhere in It.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.96,0:37:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.96,0:38:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一辆捷豹E-Type\NThis is a Jaguar E-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.76,0:38:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,1962年I系列敞篷版\NIt's a 1962 Series 1 Roadster
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.84,0:38:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,配有美妙的3.8升直六发动机\Nwith the proper 3.8-litre straight six.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.24,0:38:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.44,0:38:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这可不是一般的1962年E-Type\NAnd it's not just any 1962 E-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.16,0:38:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这辆车就是我的\NIt's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.20,0:38:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到有比这车\NAnd I can think of no car
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.84,0:38:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,更加适合这样完美的一天\Nmore perfect for a day like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.52,0:38:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁说的 我可以\NOh, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.88,0:38:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我开的是一辆V8的F-Type\NBecause I am in a V8 F-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.96,0:38:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这比哈蒙德的E-Type更快\NThis is faster than Hammond's E-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.96,0:38:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,更舒适 更经济 更可靠\NIt's more comfortable,\Nmore economical, more reliable,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有空调哦\Nmore air-conditioned
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.72,0:38:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,即使要价86,000英镑\NAnd even though it costs Ј86,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.40,0:38:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也比E-Type便宜\Nit's cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.84,0:39:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,法国佬 起床啦\NWake up, Frenchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.80,0:39:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这浪声\NOh, that's a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.68,0:39:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听见这后面的浪声吗\NCan you hear the exhausts\Nfrom back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.80,0:39:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,声音大的在威尼斯都听得到\NThey can hear them back in Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,此时此地开着这辆车\NNever has a car been more\Nperfectly tailored to its environment
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.80,0:39:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不到有比这更完美的组合了\Nthan this is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.92,0:39:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是土豪阶层的发源地\NThis is where the jetset was invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.64,0:39:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感受到我们身处一个捷豹的世界\NWe are in Jag country, I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.40,0:39:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,餐厅的账单上不可能几十年不被结账\NNot a restaurant bill will have been\Npaid around here for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.44,0:39:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只有捷豹的轮胎印能够证明他们的去处\NJust Jaguar tyre marks\Nwhere they've screeched away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.04,0:39:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我开回去拿我的钱包\N"I'm sorry.\NI'll pop off and get my wallet."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.84,0:40:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在70年代有个电视剧\NThere used to be\Na TV series in the '70s
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.20,0:40:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做The Persuaders\N由Roger Moore和Tony Curtis饰演\Ncalled The Persuaders!\Nwith Roger Moore and Tony Curtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.40,0:40:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在听这电视剧的主题曲\NAnd I'm hearing that music now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.64,0:40:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.56,0:40:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger Moore和Tony Curtis\NRoger Moore, Tony Curtis,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.48,0:40:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,开着法拉利Dino和阿斯通马丁DBS在这里穿梭\Nwhizzing about down here\Nin a Ferrari Dino
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.96,0:40:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里来回穿梭\Nand an Aston Martin DBS,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.08,0:40:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,解决各式各样的问题\Nsolving many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.28,0:40:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,比如英雄救美\Npunching men and saving womens.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正在享受这个美妙的时刻 直到\NI was enjoying it too.\NUntil...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.76,0:40:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 毕加索博物馆就在前面\NHammond, the Picasso museum's\Nalong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.72,0:40:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以停下来进去瞧瞧\NWe could stop and have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.04,0:40:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要吗 我可开着一辆捷豹呢\NReally? I'm in a Jaguar,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.32,0:40:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在法国南部开着我的E-Type\Nmy E-Type, in the south of France,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.68,0:40:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你却要我停下来参观一个\Nand you want me stop driving\Nto look at a man
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.76,0:40:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵长错地方的男人\Nwhose ears are in the wrong place?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,错了 你说的是梵高\NNo, that was Van Gogh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.60,0:40:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,毕加索是那个\NPicasso's the one who puts eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.44,0:40:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,把眼睛放错边的人\Non the wrong side of somebody's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.76,0:41:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 这是趟公路旅行\N我们来看点画作\NCome on, it's a road trip.\NLet's look at some pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己听听你刚才说了啥\NDid you not hear\Nwhat you just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.00,0:41:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场公路之旅 我们去看画画吧\N"It's a road trip.\NLet's look at some pictures."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.56,0:41:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.00,0:41:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么如此没文化？\NOh, why are you so uncultured?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.64,0:41:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在朱昂莱班 一个所有女孩\NIn Juan-les-Pins,\Nwhere all the girls have
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.08,0:41:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都特意穿着裸胸泳衣\Ncarefully designed topless swimsuits
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.16,0:41:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,圈养赛马也是仅供娱乐 的地方\Nand racehorses they keep just for fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为博一笑 哈哈哈\Nfor a laugh, a-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.36,0:41:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们停了下来 让哈蒙德能看点吃的\Nwe pulled over so Hammond could look at some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.36,0:41:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在又咋了？ -我不喜欢章鱼\N- What now?\N- I don't like octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.80,0:41:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,章鱼怎么惹你了？\NWhat's the matter with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.36,0:41:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-额.. -你想试试我的松露煎蛋卷吗？\N- Well...\N- Do you want my truffles on an omelette?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.56,0:41:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢松露 你毁了我的旅行\NDon't like truffles.\NYou are ruining this trip for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.64,0:41:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-继续 -每次我们停下来吃饭\N- Go on.\N- Every time we stop for food,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.84,0:41:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-你就逼我吃章鱼 -很好吃！\N- you make me eat octopus...\N- It's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.52,0:41:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,或是螃蟹眼睛 蜗牛腿\N...or crab's eyes or snail's legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.00,0:41:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而每次我们一上路 你就又想停下来\NAnd then every time we get going again,\Nyou make us stop again
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.28,0:41:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看一堆砖头还有什么故事里的阳台\Nto Look at a pile of bricks\Nand then that balcony from a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.68,0:42:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场公路之旅\NIt's a road trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.84,0:42:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要看风景 瞧瞧我带你来的地方\NWe're supposed to be seeing...\NLook what I've brought you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.20,0:42:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在路上\NOn the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.56,0:42:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你来的是我最喜欢的餐厅之一\NI've brought you to one of my favourite restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.92,0:42:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-海边的双人餐桌 -不是..\N- A table for two by the waterside...\N- It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.12,0:42:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了它\NEat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.52,0:42:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-这可不是舌尖上的旅行啊 -快吃\N- Not an eating trip, is it?\N- Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.56,0:42:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-把章鱼吃掉 -它刚动了\N- Eat the octopus.\N- It moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.00,0:42:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 这只是它其中的一只腿\NIt didn't. It's only one of its legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.92,0:42:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我..\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.20,0:42:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你想在服务区\NWould you like to stop\Nat a service station
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.76,0:42:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吃薯片？\Nand get some crisps?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.24,0:42:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐后 我们去了海滨散步\NAfter lunch, we went\Nfor a stroll along the seafront
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.20,0:42:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看风景\Nto look at the sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.80,0:42:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但因为这是一档老少咸宜的节目\NBut because this is a family show,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能展示看的是何种风景\Nwe can't show you\Nwhat those sights were.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.48,0:42:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然而最终 我们手里的冰激凌化得一点不剩\NEventually, though,our ice creams melted completely
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.40,0:42:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们继续上路\Nso we set off.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.76,0:43:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我们在讨论完美公路之旅\NYou know we were talking about the perfect road trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.56,0:43:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好没有开兰博基尼和布加迪来这里\NHow wrong would the Lamborghini\Nand Bugatti have been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有开福特嘉年华\NOr the Ford Fiesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.48,0:43:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.56,0:43:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于 当我们到达圣特拉斐\NThe problem is that when we arrived in Saint-Raphael,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.64,0:43:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,交通状况正如预期\Nthe traffic was predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.28,0:43:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Type也是\NAnd so was the E-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.24,0:43:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德的车听上去很虚弱\NHammond's car is sounding poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.40,0:43:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.32,0:43:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它能挺过圣特鲁佩斯的堵车吗？\NWill it be able to do the traffic jam into Saint-Tropez?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.24,0:43:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯..\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.00,0:43:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老实讲 我真的\NI'm honestly... I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.16,0:44:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很担心它 我说真的\NI am worried about her,\Nactually, I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.72,0:44:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NAre you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.16,0:44:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦天啊 听起来真不咋地\NOh, God, that doesn't sound right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.72,0:44:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,60年代的英国好声音\NThe sound of Britain in the '60s.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.88,0:44:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘠叽嘎叽嘎叽\NDing-ding-ding-ding-ding...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.68,0:44:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为中部的制造业而自豪\N"Made in the Midlands with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.68,0:44:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}(伯明翰口音)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.28,0:44:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们造出了这么漂亮的车\N"Ah, we've really put this together\Nvery nicely, we have, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.28,0:44:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的E-Type做的很好\N"Done a good job with that E-Type, we have."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.88,0:44:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,量油尺太烫了 不能摸\NOw, dipstick's too hot, can't touch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.08,0:44:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-噢 -理查德\N- Oh. - Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.44,0:44:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-干嘛 -我带了点东西给你\N- What?\N- I've bought you something
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.96,0:44:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让你高兴起来\Nto cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.20,0:44:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗？ -一个小礼物\N- Have you?\N- It's a little present.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.00,0:44:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵\NIs it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.68,0:44:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一个渔网\NIt's a fishing net.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.80,0:44:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不是E-Type的作风\NI know it's not the same as an E-Type
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.24,0:44:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在它不行了 你可以用这个\Nbut now this doesn't work any more,\Nyou can have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.72,0:44:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的渔网\NThank you for my fishing net.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.64,0:44:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要3欧元 比这车值钱\NIt's three Euros,which is more than this is worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.04,0:44:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对现在来说\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.80,0:44:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个主意\NI then had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.44,0:45:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从这里到圣特鲁佩斯来一场比赛\NWe'll have a race from here to Saint-Tropez
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.04,0:45:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们要过夜的 对吧？\Nbut we'll stay the night, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.48,0:45:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-比赛 -什么意思..\N- A race. - What...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.96,0:45:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.36,0:45:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-别管这些车了 -丢弃捷豹\N- Ditch these. - Ditch the Jags.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.72,0:45:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没得选\NYou've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.24,0:45:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,新酒店叫什么名字？巴黎大饭店\NWhat's that new hotel called?Hotel de Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.84,0:45:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-那有一个天台露天酒吧 -好的\N- It's got a rooftop bar.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.60,0:45:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,后到的人\NLast one there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.68,0:45:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿一件写着"我爱龟速船长"的衬衫\Nhas to wear an "I love James May" T-shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.64,0:45:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明天一整天\Ntomorrow, all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.44,0:45:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不小的一个处罚啊 但是..\NThat's quite a forfeit but, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.28,0:45:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一条妙计\NI have had such a brilliant idea
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.56,0:45:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克森必输无疑\Nthat Clarkson has had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.16,0:45:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我将驾驶这车去往圣特鲁佩斯\NBecause I am going to Saint-Tropez on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.52,0:45:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杜卡迪\NThe Ducati Diavel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.40,0:45:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑\NDark.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.32,0:45:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-准备就绪 哈蒙德？ -随时待命\N- Are you ready, Hammond?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.08,0:46:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,倒计时 三\NIn three,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.40,0:46:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,二  一\Ntwo, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.24,0:46:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,出发！\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.76,0:46:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很好的理由选这车\NI chose this bike for a very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.64,0:46:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎1200cc V型双缸\NThe engine, 1200cc V-twin,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.36,0:46:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,源自杜卡迪赛车1198\Ntaken from a Ducati sports bike,the 1198.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.28,0:46:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 杜卡迪知道如何制造快车\NAnd Ducati, trust me, know a thing\Nor two about making fast bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.52,0:46:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,162匹马力 英国版本\N162 brake horsepower, the UK edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.80,0:46:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在法国 被限制在100\NRestricted in France to 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.48,0:46:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你知道吗?\NBut you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.72,0:46:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但对付我今天的任务是绰绰有余了\NThat's still going to be plenty\Nfor what I want to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.96,0:46:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,极速170\NTop speed about 170,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.76,0:46:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,0到60mph加速2.5秒\N0-60 about two and a half,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.84,0:46:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 和布加迪威龙一样\Nyou know, the same as a Bugatti Veyron.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.56,0:47:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又堵了 你看\NTraffic, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.48,0:47:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么可能摆平这一切?\NHow's he going to get to even this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.20,0:47:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他永远都开不出去\NHe's never even going to\Nget out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.52,0:47:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来很帅 车又是风驰电掣\NI Look cooL. It goes Like the clappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.44,0:47:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克森就在这了\NClarkson's had it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.48,0:47:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 看到没 没车了\NThere you go. See that? Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.12,0:47:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.56,0:47:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到的是一辆菲尔兰 Squadron78游艇\NYou join me on a Fairline Squadron 78.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.52,0:47:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说78英尺长\NThat's 78 feet long.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.36,0:47:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这台机器的引擎让人难以置信\NThe engines in this thing are unbelievable,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.84,0:47:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,32升 两只涡轮增压的V12\N32-litre, twin turbocharged V12s.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.20,0:47:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,走起\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.36,0:47:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以这么开\NAnd you can drive it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.28,0:48:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,或这样\NOr like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.36,0:48:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是一艘船\NAnd because it's a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.68,0:48:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以横穿海湾抵达圣特鲁佩斯\NI could get to Saint- Tropez across the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.36,0:48:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然而哈蒙德不得不绕过海湾\NWhereas Hammond had to go all the way round it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.60,0:48:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,穿行在车流中\NSneaking through,sneaking through, just.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.12,0:48:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每一辆车\NEvery car counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.68,0:48:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,任何一辆都可能是克拉克森\NAny one of these could be Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.32,0:48:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪？\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.28,0:48:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我超过了他\NIf I have been past him,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.44,0:48:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他只能看我裹在皮衣里的屁屁感叹\Nhe would have been looking at my bottom in leather, going,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.24,0:48:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"哦 看 穿皮裤的男人屁屁" 他就好这口\N"Oh, look, a man's bottom in leather."\NHe's obsessed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.68,0:48:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道理查德哈蒙德在开什么\NI don't know what Richard Hammond is using,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.12,0:48:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我猜\Nbut I'm guessing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.80,0:48:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是一辆摩托车之类的\Nit's a motorcycle of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.88,0:48:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他会从头到脚都是裹着牛皮\NSo he'll be dressed from head to foot in leather,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.16,0:48:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,恼火于交通堵塞\Nfurious at the traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.76,0:48:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股这样..\Nwith his bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.24,0:48:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我啊 我在开摩托车\N"Look at me, I'm on a motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.68,0:48:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跨下一个震动的机器\N"I'm straddling a throbbing machine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.00,0:49:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会那么做\NI'm not doing any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.68,0:49:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,导航带我们驶向圣特鲁佩斯\NGot the satnav down here to bring us\Nonto the bearing of Saint-Tropez.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.60,0:49:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想再快一点\NI'm just going to take it up\Na little bit more,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.40,0:49:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,2300转\N2,300 rpm a side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.40,0:49:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧呀 看看这个！\NLook at this. Look at this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.00,0:49:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我的柴油吧 哈蒙德\NEat my diesel, Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.60,0:49:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想弯过一个转角\NI just want to come round\None of these corners
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.92,0:49:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看见一辆迈凯轮12C\Nand see a McLaren 12C.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.76,0:49:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或者 SLS黑色系\NOr an SLS Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.04,0:49:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且被堵的死死的 然后我超过他\NAnd he will be stuck. And I will pass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.32,0:49:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要问问他 "摩托车\NAnd I will ask him, "Mmm, bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.84,0:49:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够好?"\N"Still no good?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.68,0:50:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有人要喝点吗？\NAnyone fancy a drink in the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.36,0:50:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-要不要？ -好\N- Yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.76,0:50:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.72,0:50:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,非常谢谢\NThanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.00,0:50:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又堵车了 又堵车了\NStanding traffic. Standing traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.44,0:50:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 克拉克森 你在哪?\NCome on, Clarkson, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.12,0:50:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这要没人突然打开门或者左转\NAs long as nobody opens their door\Nor suddenly turns left,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.04,0:50:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我就可以一直这样飚下去\NI can just keep hacking through it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.00,0:50:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧 这就有个开门的\NOh, there you go. That's the door open.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.04,0:50:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一个\NThat's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.80,0:50:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,总有人会这样 总有一个\NThat's the fella. There's always one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.92,0:50:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他会在任何这些车里 我随时都可能看见他\NHe's going to be in any one of these. Any minute now I'm going to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.80,0:50:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这肯定是他了\NThis has got to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.92,0:50:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 你好 杰里米·克拉克森\NLadies and gentlemen, hello, Jeremy Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.48,0:50:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 不是他\NNo. That's not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.32,0:50:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当Squadron正卯足了劲前进\NWith the Squadron at full chat
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.40,0:50:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,圣特鲁佩斯近在咫尺\Nand Saint-Tropez very close indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.20,0:50:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,船上的时光也美好极了\Nlife on the boat was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.36,0:51:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,咕噜噜！\NGrunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.20,0:51:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这让它更像一辆杜卡迪了\NThis is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.80,0:51:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不断地前行中\NGetting a proper move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.52,0:51:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,解决了最差劲的圣拉斐尔的交通\NHaving cleared the worst of the Saint-Raphael traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.68,0:51:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在正飞速行驶在开阔的道路上\NI was now on the open road\Nand closing fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.12,0:51:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 老实讲\NOkay, there is, I'll be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.20,0:51:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只有很小很小的可能性\Na tiny, tiny chance
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.76,0:51:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他从堵塞的交通中开出城市\Nhe got through all of that traffic and out of town
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.40,0:51:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在这里横扫千军万马\Nand then caned it along here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.56,0:51:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而我还没赶上他\Nand I simply haven't caught him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.20,0:51:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有理由相信\NBut I've got a good suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.12,0:51:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们到达圣特鲁佩斯\Nwhen we get to Saint-Tropez,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.96,0:51:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿交通会更糟 我就能找到他了\Nthere'll be more traffic\Nand that is where I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.88,0:51:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要将78英尺长的船泊入圣特鲁佩斯港口\NI'm about to park my 78-foot boat in Saint-Tropez harbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.28,0:51:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我唯一的劣势\NThis is the only slow bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.68,0:51:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,进港太慢\Nthe wobbling about\Nin Saint-Tropez harbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.64,0:51:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们有个傻X的限速\N'Cause they've got some stupid speed limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.44,0:51:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天啊 看哪\NOh, good God, Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.36,0:52:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,堵得水泄不通\NTraffic. That's a big jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.68,0:52:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喔!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.68,0:52:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,见缝插针 过过过\NSqueezing through, coming through,\Ncoming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.20,0:52:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当哈蒙德还在\NAs Hammond weaved his way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.88,0:52:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,圣特鲁佩斯常年的堵车中挣扎\Nthrough the annual Saint-Tropez traffic jam...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.52,0:52:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我天啊\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.76,0:52:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在等待被安排一个泊位\NI was still waiting to be given a parking space.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.32,0:52:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,过了 过了\NThrough, coming through, coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.48,0:52:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎大饭店 谢谢你\NHotel de Paris, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.48,0:52:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟!\NMate!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.04,0:52:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样?\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.00,0:53:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么...\NHow...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.76,0:53:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你流了好多汗\NGod, you look sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.60,0:53:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么特么可能?\NHow the bloody hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.36,0:53:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看见你啊 我一次都没有看到你\NI didn't see you.I didn't see you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.12,0:53:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了一台F12 我以为是你\NI saw a Ferrari F12,I thought it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.88,0:53:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是\NThing is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.12,0:53:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有摩托车驾照\Nyou've got a motorcycle licence.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.84,0:53:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-是 -而哥手里\N- Yes. - Well, now, I have
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.16,0:53:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有游艇驾照\Na boat Licence.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.52,0:53:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当然这就意味着明天嘛\NAnd what this means, of course,is tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.68,0:53:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你会穿上一件很酷的T恤\Nwhile you'll be wearing a T-shirt\Nand that'll be cooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.00,0:53:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我忘了还有这\NAh, I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.12,0:53:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写着"我爱龟速船长"\N...it will say "I love James May" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.28,0:53:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早上 哈蒙德一点也不急于\NThe next morning,Hammond was in no hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.64,0:53:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,离开酒店\Nto leave the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.40,0:53:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -干啥?\N- Hammond.- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.20,0:53:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-出来啊哈蒙德 -不要\N- Hammond, come out. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.84,0:53:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,内什么 我还在收拾行装\NNo, I'm a bit...I haven't... I'm just packing my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.76,0:53:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-已经8点45了 -我还在收拾\N- It's quarter to 9:00.\N- Yeah, I'm just packing my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.52,0:53:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在收拾\NI'm packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.60,0:54:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我身体不太舒服\NActually, no, I'm not very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.32,0:54:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,外面没什么人啊\NThere's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.56,0:54:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-我感觉很糟糕 -哈蒙德!\N- I'm poorly.- Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.80,0:54:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我要出来了\NRight. I'm coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.36,0:54:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啧啧啧啧\NOoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.24,0:54:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 看啊\NNow, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.96,0:54:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-这太糟糕了 -是啊\N- This is bad. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.92,0:54:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我认为接下来的消息是更糟糕的\NBut I'm afraid the news gets even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.16,0:54:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不会更糟了吧\NIt can't be any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.72,0:54:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被选择了同样的车\NWe've both chosen the same car.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.28,0:54:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是并不糟糕啊 不是么?\NWell, that's not so bad, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.48,0:54:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说只有一台车? -是啊\N- You mean there's only one?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.92,0:54:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 圣特罗佩街头\NSo, Saint-Tropez,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.92,0:54:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,二男 一敞篷宾利\Nconvertible Bentley, two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.36,0:54:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我们看上去有点\NOh, we are looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.16,0:54:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我才意识到\NJust realised.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.08,0:54:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,两个男人坐在一台宾利里面\NTwo men in a Bentley.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.68,0:54:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,并不只是宾利让我们很显眼\NIt isn't just the Bentley,\Nwe ought to make that plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.96,0:55:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而是敞篷的问题\NIt's any convertible.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.08,0:55:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,任何两个男人坐进一部敞篷车\NPut two men in a convertible car,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.36,0:55:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,打开车顶之后 问题立刻就出现了\Ntake the roof off and instantly, questions are raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.20,0:55:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 至少在车里 别人看不见我的T恤\NStill, at least in the car, they couldn't see my T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.48,0:55:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,直到\NUntil...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.56,0:55:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么在这停车?\NWhy are you pulling over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.04,0:55:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看点东西\NI just want to have a look at something.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.12,0:55:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-看啥? -就是一些东西嘛\N-What? -Just stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.08,0:55:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么东西 -呃 我想看看那些船\N- What stuff? -Just... I want to look at the boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.96,0:55:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要干什么\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.04,0:55:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-这地方不错啊 -我不想停下来\N- It's a nice place.\N- I don't want to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.88,0:55:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-这么多人... -出来啊\N- There's people......- Just get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.04,0:55:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要 -要\N-No. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.28,0:55:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要! -要!\N-No! -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.48,0:55:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我要躲起来\NNo, I'm going to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.04,0:55:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要出去 我就钻进去\NI'm not getting out.\NI'm getting in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.24,0:55:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就剩下我自己了\NI'm on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.00,0:55:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,额滴神啊\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.16,0:55:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算走远点丢下他\NI'm just going to go for a walk and leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.64,0:55:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快结束这一切吧\NMake this end.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.92,0:56:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是打赌输了嘛\NI Lost a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.48,0:56:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.92,0:56:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大猩猩我们可以走了么?\NJeremy, can we go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.28,0:56:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.04,0:56:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这些游艇哪个有螺旋桨\NDo any of these boats have propellers
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.64,0:56:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有哪个现在就可以启动离开的?\Nand are any of them likely\Nto be running right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.84,0:56:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,又是拍照的 这里八卦围观群众还真多\NPaparazzi again.There's quite a lot of paps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.80,0:56:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们赶紧走吧\NYeah. So let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.64,0:56:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是出现了一个小问题\NThere was, however,a small problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.00,0:56:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-是在这里么\N-本来就是在这个地方吧\N-Was it... -Is this where it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.08,0:56:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊 -显然现在不在了\N- Yes. - Well, it's not, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.84,0:56:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你原因吧\NI tell you why it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.20,0:56:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是不能停车的\NYou can't park here, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.12,0:56:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你能在这里停车么? 被允许的么...什么?\NCan you park here?Are you allowed to... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.00,0:56:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能在这停啊 旁边画了一个车被拖走的图\NNo, you can't park here or that's a picture of a car being towed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.04,0:56:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道 我真的是 -车被拖走了?\N- Do you know, I genuinely...\N- Has the car been towed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.56,0:56:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NWell, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.84,0:56:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这等我\NJust you wait here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.32,0:56:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我去取车\Nand I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.40,0:56:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-放松点 -好吧\N- Just relax. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.32,0:56:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有多远啊 我会在一个小时之内回来\NIt's not far, actually, I'll be back in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.64,0:57:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信此时此刻应该会有一个人比我更悲催\NI'm sure somebody somewhere at some time has been unhappier.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.68,0:57:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,两小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.00,0:57:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了 求你了 求你了\NPlease, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.00,0:57:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点也没意思 一点也没意思\NNo, not funny. Not even halfway funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.28,0:57:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米把这该死的车门打开\NOpen the damn door.\NJeremy, open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.16,0:57:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的?\NHow do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.64,0:57:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我进来了\NI'm getting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.36,0:57:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你也许会疑惑\NNow, at this point you may be wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.32,0:57:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们两人都选择了宾利\Nwhy both of us chose a Bentley.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.04,0:57:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一部分原因是我们认为现在的宾利很漂亮\NWell, partly it's because we think that these days, it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.52,0:57:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是 现在还装备了一台\NBut mostly it's because it's now available
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.80,0:57:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,更轻量化 而且声浪更棒的4升V8发动机\Nwith a brilliant lighter, louder 4-litre V8.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.04,0:57:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但哈蒙德脑中最惦记的却不是这个\NNot that this was foremost in Hammond's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.80,0:57:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-杰瑞米克拉克森 -到\N- Jeremy Clarkson. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.84,0:57:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是把我的座椅加热开到最大了?\NHave you put my seat heater on full?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.80,0:57:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:57:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 老兄这实在是\NOh, mate, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.08,0:58:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-哦耶! 整到你了 -哦!\N- Yes! Result. - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.36,0:58:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了\NJust horrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.72,0:58:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-这就是我想要的结果 -哦!\N- That's a result right there. - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.64,0:58:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我得到了另外一个期待的结果\NThen I got another result.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.56,0:58:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一条干净的 开放公路\NA clear, open road.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.80,0:58:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会有一点颠\N"It's got a bit of poke."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.32,0:58:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-哦哦 -这就是本来就该有的声音\N- Whoa! - Oh, that's how it should sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.80,0:58:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是怎样的感觉么?\NDo you know what it feels like?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.08,0:58:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-一台跑车应有的感觉 -是啊\N- An sportscar. - It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.24,0:58:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我的座椅加热打开了么?\NHave you put my seat heater on?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.00,0:58:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\NYes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.80,0:58:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在是对不...\NI'm really sor...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.80,0:58:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是一台很棒的车\NIt's a machine, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.76,0:58:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 靓车!\NHello, machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.16,0:59:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这款车让我喜欢的一个主要原因就是\NOne of the reasons why I like this car so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.68,0:59:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,与宾利的徽章无关\Nyou know it isn't just a Bentley badge,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.80,0:59:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这款车克服了众多的工程难题\Nthere's some properly difficult\Nengineering that's gone into this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.00,0:59:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米 你是不是又把我的座椅加热打开了\NJeremy, have you put my seat heater on again? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.36,0:59:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点也不\NThat's not... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.24,0:59:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.36,0:59:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我坐的高一点\N别人就能把我的T恤看的更清楚\NAnd if I lift myself up,they can see my T-shirt better
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.16,0:59:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我坐下去就被烤焦了  上帝啊!\Nand if I sit down, I cook. God!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.84,0:59:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明的引擎\NSo, clever engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.48,0:59:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,智能的四驱系统\Nclever four-wheel-drive system,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.36,0:59:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最近越来越漂亮的外观\Nlooks a lot better these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.32,0:59:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,美妙的声浪\NGreat noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.52,0:59:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,美妙的声浪\NGreat noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.68,0:59:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一台伟大的车子\NIt's a great car.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.16,0:59:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是 这车仍然有鲁尼的味道\NThe problem it has still is that Rooney flavour.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.16,0:59:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我说鲁尼的味道是指\NThe whiff of Wayne means
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.04,0:59:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,开着它出现 你会感觉不好意思\Nyou do feel embarrassed to turn up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.16,0:59:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德!\NHammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.24,0:59:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再打开我的座椅加热了\NStop putting my seat heater on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.36,1:00:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管座椅和车辆与日头一样热辣\NSoon, despite the hot seats,\Nthe hot car and the hot sun,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.56,1:00:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是气氛开始变得冷凝了\Nthe atmosphere became frosty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.44,1:00:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我们决定分开\NSo we decided to split up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.44,1:00:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定去看一座现在已经大部分坍塌的建筑\NAnd then I decided to look at a building that had mostly fallen over.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.12,1:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊\NLook at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.16,1:00:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面有头野猪 看啊\NYes, look, there's a wild boar,there we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.52,1:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一幅狩猎图\NThis is a hunting scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.24,1:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 这有一幅狩猎图!\NHammond, there's a hunting scene!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.16,1:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德!\NHammond!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.72,1:00:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该是一座陵寝\NIt's like there's a mausoleum
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.84,1:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-有类似于凯旋门的拱门\N-别跟我说话 我不在乎\N- and a sort of triumphal arch.\N- Don't talk to me, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.24,1:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想听 我也不想知道 我真的不想!\NI don't want to hear about it.\NI don't want to know, I really don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.76,1:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了\NI'm sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.96,1:01:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太荒唐了 我吃了螃蟹的眼睛\NThis is ridiculous. I've eaten crab's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.88,1:01:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了一座来自于故事当中的阳台\N说真的 现在开始 我要做主了\NI've looked at a balcony from a story.\NNo, seriously, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.28,1:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我决定下一步要做什么了\NIt's my turn to decide what we do next.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.04,1:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接下来要做的就是去跑拉力赛\NAnd what we're doing next is going rally driving.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.04,1:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 开总裁去跑拉力? -不是\N- What, in a Maserati Quattroporte?- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.12,1:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-那就是用幻影? -也不是\N- And a Rolls-Royce Phantom?- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.84,1:01:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个好主意\NI've had a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.00,1:01:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是桑布尔赛道\NThis is the circuit Sambre,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.56,1:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,充满了法国拉力赛的残酷考验\Nendless kilometres of unrelenting French rally stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.96,1:01:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,试替哥对这里了如指掌\NAnd a place The Stig knows well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.96,1:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-要怎样 -这个嘛\N- What? - Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.64,1:01:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是试替哥的避暑山庄啊\Nthis is The Stig's summer retreat, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.52,1:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每年夏天他都来这边 干这个\NHe comes here every year and does that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.96,1:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-而且他说... -你说干这个是什么意思\N- And he says... - What do you mean, he does that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.32,1:01:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在冬天 他去开雪地赛道\N夏天一到 他就来这儿\NWell, in winter he goes ice racing.\NSummer, he comes here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.72,1:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三个礼拜 不停的干这个\NThree weeks of that he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.28,1:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 都不带休息? -对 钻进汽车 三个礼拜\N- What, non-stop? -Yeah, gets in the car, three weeks,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.20,1:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,三礼拜后 钻出汽车 回家\Nand then three weeks later,\Ngets out, goes home.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.92,1:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他的假日\N不管怎样 他说我们可以用这个赛道\NThat's his holiday. Anyway, he says we could use it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.72,1:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来开拉力\Nto do our rally driving.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.00,1:01:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-天太热了 -啊哈\N- It's too hot. - Dah!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.64,1:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我正好也想到这个问题了\NI have actually thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.16,1:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-你喜欢敞篷车不是么 -没错\N- You like a convertible, don't you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.76,1:02:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们干嘛不用敞篷车来开拉力呢\NWhy don't we rally-drive convertibles?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.00,1:02:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-灰尘太多 -拜托 就帮我这一次忙\N- It's too dusty. - Now, do one thing for me,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.36,1:02:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出去弄两辆敞篷车\Nwe're going to go and get\Nsome convertibles,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.76,1:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们改装成拉力车 然后干这个!\Nturn them into rally cars and do that!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.04,1:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会开拉力赛啊\NI can't do rally driving.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.76,1:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-很简单啊 你只要... -我干不来啊!\N- It's easy, just... - I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.72,1:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我在没抓地力的路面上不会...\NI can't drive on loose surfaces...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.70,1:02:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,过了很久
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.68,1:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的选择\NThis is what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.60,1:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,尼桑 350Z\NNissan 350Z.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.32,1:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,3.5升V6\NThree-and-a-half-litre V6,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.68,1:02:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,276匹马力 后轮驱动\N276 brake horsepower, rear-wheel drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.84,1:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能看着它 心想\NNow, you might be looking\Nat it, thinking, "Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.20,1:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它看上去不太像拉力车啊\N"it doesn't look much like a rally car."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.28,1:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但别急 这车可是Datsun 240Z的\NBut hold on,this car is a direct descendant
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.08,1:02:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,直系后代\Nof the Datsun 240Z,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.80,1:02:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是曾经统治过国际拉力赛场的赛车\Na car that owned world rallying.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.52,1:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这车可谓血统纯正\NSo this has got history.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.52,1:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它必定会表现得很棒\NIt's going to be brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.84,1:03:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我选了一辆宝马\NI've got a BMW.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.04,1:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有半点拉力血统\N这也是我喜欢它的原因\NNo history of rallying at all,\Nit's one of the reasons I like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.20,1:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 给我们说说它多大排量\NWell, come on, tell us about it,\Nwhat engine has it got?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.08,1:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,2.5升直6\NTwo-and-a-half-litre straight 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.76,1:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比尼桑少了一升 马力呢?\N1000cc less than the Nissan. Power?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.60,1:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,192?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.52,1:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大概少了80 扭矩呢？\NThat's about 80 horsepower less. Torque?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.08,1:03:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,180\N180.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.16,1:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-大概也少了80 -很好!\N- That's about 80 torques less. - Good!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.56,1:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-很好是什么意思 -就是很好\N-What do you mean, "good"? -Good!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.96,1:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米 你在这事上还没进入竞争状态啊\NJeremy, you're not really getting into the competitive spirit of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.08,1:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢在没有摩擦力的地方开车\NI don't like driving without friction!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.40,1:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敞篷拉力赛会马上成为下一个热点\NOpen-top rally is going to be the next big thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.64,1:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们赶紧把这些车改装成拉力车去\NLet's go and convert these into rally cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.56,1:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我们要找到个车间 然后放音乐\NThis meant finding a workshop and cueing the music.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.76,1:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定\NGot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.52,1:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 赞\NOh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.68,1:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我真厉害\NGod, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.36,1:03:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就应该能把我和理查德在马力上\NThat will make up for the horsepower deficit
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.36,1:03:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,的差距补回来了\Nthat I have on Richard's car.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.42,1:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,手写"涡轮"\NTURBO
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.12,1:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,八月先生\NThis is August.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.64,1:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,四月先生\NNow Mr April.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.64,1:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}可怜的五月先生Mr. May
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.04,1:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的防滚架搞定了\NMy roll-cage is complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.44,1:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天 我们的战车蓄势待发\NThe next day,\Nour cars were ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.28,1:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天气也一样\N- And so was the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.28,1:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太棒了\NThis is all just fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.28,1:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,突然间 就变成了完美的拉力天气\NSuddenly, perfect rallying\Nweather is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.16,1:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一点小雨 泥泞 山上还有点雾气\NBit of rain, mud, mist on the hills,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.84,1:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的车也状态完美\Nand my car is now perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.38,1:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(383.197,404)}好一坨翔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.24,1:04:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有改得过头\NHaven't gone over the top\Nwith the modifications.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.44,1:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,新轮毂 新轮胎 防滚架\NNew wheels, new tyres, roll-cage,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.96,1:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,赞助商贴纸 BBC要求不能用真的\Nsponsorship stickers,\Ncan't have real ones,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.08,1:04:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们伪造了赞助商 让你感受赛车的氛围\NBBC objects, but we've made 'em up\Nto put you in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.84,1:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,车内 赛车座椅 四点式安全带 足够了\NInside, racing seat,\Nfull harness, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.12,1:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该是完美的一天\NThis is going to be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.98,1:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(162.507,572)}屁眼医生
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.36,1:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我就照他抄了\NI just copied him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.52,1:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在他就要在泥地里开他的达特桑了\NAnd now he's going to drive about\Nin his Datsun in the mud.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.08,1:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的没错 我等不及了\NHe was right I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.60,1:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 爽\NOh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.40,1:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天上下雨 我在跑拉力赛 真是完美啊\NIt's actually raining, I'm in a rally.\NThis is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.44,1:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在吃了一路这么多傻缺食物 看了那么多石头后\NAfter all the stupid food\Nand looking at rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.04,1:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能够在这里干这样一件由衷让人激动\N而且如此真实的事情\Nto come out and do something\Ngenuinely exciting and real and...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.88,1:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我复活了\NI've come alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.80,1:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷 爽\NOh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.96,1:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,理查德 现在 还在外面\NHammond is out now in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.52,1:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人已经疯了!\NThe man is insane!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.12,1:06:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 让我再爽爽 来啊\NBring it on, let's have more. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.60,1:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这还叫下雨?\NYou call that rain?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.92,1:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喔吼吼吼\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.52,1:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是当下全世界我最喜欢的地方\NThis is my favourite place\Nin the world now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.64,1:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.72,1:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 理查德 给我解释一下\NI'm sorry, Hammond,\Ndo try to explain it to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.00,1:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么也弄不明白\N'cause I'm struggling to get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.16,1:06:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是好一阵子以来 我最欢乐的时光\NIt's about the most fun\NI've had in a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.88,1:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解为什么试替哥会来这儿了\NI can see why The Stig comes here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.76,1:06:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-你浑身都是泥啊 -没错\N- You're covered in mud.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.48,1:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-天上还打着响雷啊 -没错我知道\N- There's a massive thunderstorm raging.\N- Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.04,1:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 就连天气也比前几天要好 完美极了\NI know, even the weather's better here.\NIt's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.08,1:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你说比前几天要好是什么意思\NWhat do you mean, it's better?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.58,1:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-理查德 我真必须要这么干么 -没错\N- Hammond, do I have to do this?\N- Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.46,1:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(985.079,520)}屁眼俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.36,1:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天听我的 这就是我们今天要做的事情\NIt's my thing today,\Nand this is what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.76,1:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 为了表明我多么的有肚量\NAnd so, to show\Nwhat a good sport I am,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.96,1:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我满足他\NI obliged.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.76,1:07:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦老天爷\NOh, God's truth!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.00,1:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦疼疼疼\NOh! That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.84,1:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 不舒服\NSo, discomfort...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷这简直太让人不爽了\NOh! That's just horrible!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.08,1:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,危险\NDanger.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.52,1:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,凄惨 冷\NMisery, cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.16,1:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,以30km/h的时速滑行\NSlithering around at 21 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.48,1:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦去他娘的...\NOh, no! Bloody...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.56,1:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我被淋了一身屎浆\NI've just had a brown shower.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.80,1:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是最后一根稻草\NThat really was the final straw.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.08,1:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我发现这居然不是\NAnd then it turned out it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.32,1:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们跑过了 熟悉了这个赛道\NSo, we got the hang of it,\Nwe now know the course, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.16,1:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,下面是计时赛\NTime for timed laps.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.80,1:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么 -那 接下来开始计时\N- What?\N- Well, we do timed laps now,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.12,1:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样来 如果我们各开十圈\Nthat's what we do.\NI reckon if we do 10 each
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.52,1:07:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就能看出我们的稳定性如何\Nand then we can just work out\Nhow consistent we are,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.72,1:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟在哪里能快上个几秒 没错吧\Nwhere we can just\Nshave those extra seconds out, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.72,1:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明天 你要被我逼着吃\NTomorrow, you are going to eat
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.00,1:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,獾的左蛋蛋\Na badger's left teste.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.00,1:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}蜜獾习惯直接攻击人类蛋蛋 咬下然后逃跑
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.48,1:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 无视常识的我们\NAnd so, flying\Nin the face of common sense,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.44,1:08:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,又回到了赛道上\Nwe got back out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.24,1:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,计时赛 所以真的是非常关键\NTimed laps now, so it's really critical
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.36,1:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要足够勇敢 持续踩下油门\Nto just be brave enough\Nto keep that power in.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.72,1:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,计时赛 那有什么意义啊\NWhat's the point\Nof timed laps?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.60,1:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他比我多了80 嗷... 多了80bhp\NHe's got 80 more horsepower...\NOh! ...more than I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.48,1:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他开拉力比我厉害\NHe's better at it than I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.48,1:08:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有一套限滑差速器\NAnd he's got\Na limited-slip differential.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.32,1:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有那东西\NI haven't got one of those.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.60,1:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 在过弯的时候 根本控制不了\N一个轮子在不停空转\NSo, when I go round the corner,\None wheel spins and that's It.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.28,1:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喔吼吼吼 操控正确的时候感觉真是太爽了\NWoo-hoo! God, it feels\Ngood when you get it right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.40,1:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.92,1:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷 嗷 天啊\NOh! Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.16,1:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他会被...哈哈哈哈\NHe will have been...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.84,1:09:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦他开过来了 我从这就能看到他的牙齿\NOh, here he comes,\NI can see his teeth from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.56,1:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 在拉力赛道上超车 这可不多见\NRight, overtaking on a rally stage.\NThis is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.32,1:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦他要超过去了\NOh, he's coming through!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.84,1:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不 那个小不点伯明翰人超过去了\NOh, no! The hideous little Brummie\Nhas torn past!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.40,1:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈 套你一圈\NA-ha! Got you!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.80,1:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦他过去了 他把各种情况...\NOh, he's done it......\NOh, he's just made everything
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.92,1:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更糟了 我啥都看不见了\Nmuch worse now, I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.80,1:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜上全是泥\NMuddy goggles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.60,1:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想弄断他胯下的所有骨头\NEvery bone in his crotch,\Nthat is what I'm going to break.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.48,1:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷 呸\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.72,1:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没过多久 天气变得更坏了\NSoon, the weather got so bad,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.60,1:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,连理查德也看不清赛道了\Neven Hammond couldn't\Nsee where he was going.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.52,1:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,操 操 嗷\NShit! Shit! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.84,1:10:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 他建议我们休息 来一顿特制的拉力午餐\NSo, he suggested we stop\Nfor one of his special rallying lunches.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.68,1:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 赞 大吃一顿\NMmm. Okay, tuck in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.96,1:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的? -嗯嗯\N- Really?\N- Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.92,1:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吃这个是因为当地以热狗出名的么\N'Cause this part of France\Nis famous for its hotdogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.28,1:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它上面可是有法国芥末\NIt's got French mustard on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.52,1:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊 -等一下\N- Yeah...\N- Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.60,1:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.88,1:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这个香肠里有什么吧\NYou do know what's\Nin that sausage, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.36,1:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-香肠啊 -猪的指甲\N- Sausage.\N- Pigs' toenails,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.60,1:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睫毛\Neyelashes...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.28,1:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴给我好好享受 不管怎样\N在你享受的时候 我拿到了我们的圈速\NShut up and enjoy it. And, anyway, while\Nyou enjoy it, I've got the timings here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.40,1:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我大约在1分16 1分13这个水平\NI'm around the 1:16, 1:13,\Nthat kind of mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.04,1:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯哼 -你在1分53 1分46\N- Mmm-hmm.\N- You're 1:53, 1:46...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.88,1:10:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我耳朵里都进泥了\NI've got soil in my ears!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.76,1:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1分35 1分40 所以基本上很明确\N135, 140... Basically, what this\Nis showing is that I am clearly
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.00,1:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我比你强太多了\Na lot better at this than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.08,1:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-我和你做个交易 -什么\N-I'll do you a deal.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.52,1:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再开一圈\NWe will do one more lap.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.44,1:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,决一死战的一圈\NDo-or-die lap.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.44,1:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我开得比你快的话 我们立刻走人\NIf I'm faster, we leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.20,1:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-如果你比我快 -对\N-If you're faster than me?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.48,1:10:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好 如果我比你快 我们一直开到天黑\NAll right, well, if I'm faster,\Nwe carry on till dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.76,1:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-你觉得怎样 -嗯嗯\N- You'll do that?\N- Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.32,1:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的? -嗯嗯\N- Seriously?\N- Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.04,1:11:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.64,1:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我先出发\NI went first.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.80,1:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,3 2 1 出发(法语)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.24,1:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,出发了\NAnd we're off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.76,1:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我不光想要赢他 我还想羞辱他\NRight, now, I don't want to just\Nbeat him, I want to humiliate him.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.64,1:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦耶 就应该这样\NOh, yes! That was correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.24,1:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喔!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.48,1:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才下面有一个巨大的坑啊\NThat was a monstrous dump\Nfrom below there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.80,1:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大自然也加入了我们\NNature is joining in with us now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.44,1:11:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是欢乐无比啊\NOh, this is just epically good fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.56,1:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好了杰里米 我觉得你要是只比我慢1分以内\NAll right, Jeremy, I reckon if you get\Nwithin a minute of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.84,1:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很惊讶的 你没机会了\NI'll be staggered. Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.56,1:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我自信满满\NFilled with determination,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.28,1:12:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,策"马"阵前 准备出击\NI lined up the BMW on the start line.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.36,1:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,3 2 1 出发
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.04,1:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 我绝对会赢\NRight, I am going to win this
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.44,1:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就不用再干这个了\Nand then we can stop doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.80,1:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这会是...噢慢着\NThat's... Oh! Hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.56,1:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,耶\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.52,1:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\NWhat do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.64,1:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄的干活 打枪的不要\NSneaky beaky. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.76,1:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,耶!\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.36,1:12:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,连老天爷都站在我这边\NThe gods are on my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.48,1:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这回的圈速绝对慢不了\NThis is going to be one hell of a Lap!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.64,1:12:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,随后我们一起去看我们跑的怎么样\NWe then met up to see how we'd done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.36,1:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 你的成绩是1分17秒3\NRichard Hammond, you did\Nit in one minute, 17.3.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.92,1:13:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然比不上我的最快圈速 但也不算慢\N已经是个很高的起点了\N- Not my fastest but not bad.\N- Well, it was a standing start.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.44,1:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是 绝对的 -继续 然后呢\NIt was, yes, of course it was.\NYes, go on, them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.68,1:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是 28秒 -多少\N- Me, 28 seconds...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.88,1:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一分多少\NOne minute what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.20,1:13:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一分 就是28秒\N28 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.80,1:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能连一分钟都不到\NHow did you find a minute in the...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.36,1:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-不可能吧 -只能说我是终极驾驶机器\N- I mean...\N- Ultimate driving machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.40,1:13:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有宝马Z4的功劳\NAnd a BMW Z4.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.48,1:13:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.16,1:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我立马开溜\NI left immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.72,1:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后踏上了前往波城的最后350英里\NAnd set off on the 350-mile drive to Pau
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.84,1:13:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶着一辆V12阿斯顿马丁\Nin a V12 Aston Martin.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.44,1:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而哈蒙德开着一辆大众甲壳虫\NHammond, meanwhile,\Nwas in a Volkswagen Beetle
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.32,1:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和往常一样抱怨着\Nand moaning, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.00,1:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他这个作弊已经无法无天了\NHis cheating is getting out of control.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.16,1:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话还有什么意思\N要是他动不动就用Stig做替身\NThere's no point doing anything\Nif he's just going to borrow The Stig
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.48,1:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,或者抄近路 这是我能想到的唯一可能性\Nor cut a corner, which I can only\Nimagine is what he did in that instance.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.80,1:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定抄了一条相当近的路 这也太明显了吧\NIt must have been one hell\Nof a corner, he can't even cheat well!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.72,1:14:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认我那近路抄的有点夸张\NI admit my shortcut was a bit short.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.56,1:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且耗时有点短得离谱 不过看看好的一面\NAnd the time was a bit implausible.\NBut look,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.44,1:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅天气好多了\N我现在还开上了阿斯顿马丁Vanquish\Nthe weather is improving and now\NI'm in an Aston Martin Vanquish.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.88,1:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这车真心了不起\NThis is a truly magnificent car.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.32,1:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,算是这么长时间以来最好的一辆马丁\NBest Aston yet by a long way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.88,1:14:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它是介于狂野的DBS和温和的Virage\NIt's a blend of the hardcore DBS
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.48,1:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,之间的一种调和\Nand the slightly softer Virage.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.12,1:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是太完美了\NIt's just tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.96,1:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下面我就要请出哈蒙德\NAnd now I shall hand you\Nover to Richard Hammond,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.40,1:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来向你解释为什么他那辆保时捷911\Nwho shall try to explain\Nwhy the Porsche 911
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.68,1:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在某些鬼知道的方面\Nthat he's driving\Nis in some way different
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.56,1:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟所有老款的911有什么不同\Nto all the Porsche 911s\Nthat have gone before.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.80,1:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他居然还有脸说911都长一个样\NHow can he go on about 911s\Nall being the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.12,1:15:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那咱们来看看所谓的阿斯顿马丁 系列\NLet me talk you through\Nthe Aston Martin range.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.72,1:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Vantage V8, V12 Vantage,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.64,1:15:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,DB9  DBS  Virage 还有前面那货\NDB9, DBS, Virage, that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.24,1:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那才叫一个模子里刻出来的吧\Nthey're all exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.16,1:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿斯顿马丁设计了这个造型\NAston Martin came up with the design.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.32,1:15:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们觉得 哎 这看起来不错\Nthought, "Oh, that looks pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.84,1:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不如给它起不同的名字吧\N这样就会有更多的人来买了\N"Let's call it lots of different things\Nand then more people will buy it."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.84,1:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,眼前就是个例子\NIt's just another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.28,1:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,同一辆车取名为C2 C2S C4 C4S\NC2, C2S, C4, C4S,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.36,1:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以叫GT2 GT3 Turbo 997 996 993\NGT2, GT3, Turbo, 997, 996, 993...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.88,1:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,新911的型号叫991\NThe new 911 is called the 991,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.20,1:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,车身比上一代要更宽更长\Nit's longer and wider\Nthan the previous 911.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.24,1:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,新引擎 新变速箱 新内饰和新的转向系统\NIt's got a new engine, new gear box,\Nnew interior and new steering.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.92,1:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最关键的地方 911第一次\NThis is the critical point,\Nfor the first time,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.40,1:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,使用了电子转向而不是液压转向\Nthe steering is electric\Nrather than purely hydraulic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.44,1:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就当我刚刚找着状态的时候\NJust as I was getting into the groove,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.96,1:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,杰里米又找了个地方停下了\NJeremy pulled off again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.16,1:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你又干嘛啊\NWhat now?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.84,1:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们明天就要到波城了\NWell, I thought it would be a good idea,\Nsince we're at Pau tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.92,1:16:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该重新熟悉一下\Nto reacquaint ourselves with the concept
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.72,1:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在摩擦力作用下驾驶的概念\Nof driving while under\Nthe influence of friction.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.76,1:16:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢摩擦力\NI don't like friction.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.92,1:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,波城啊哥们 那可是波城\NPau, mate. It's Pau.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.24,1:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人家从1901年就开始赛车了\NThey've been racing there since 1901.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.24,1:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fangio曾经在那里比过赛\NFangio has raced there,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.88,1:16:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有Jim Clark Jackie Stewart\N那可不是一个随便的地方\NJim Clark, Jackie Stewart.\NThis is a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.52,1:16:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是 好比所有汽车爱好者的伯利恒圣城\NThis is... It's Bethlehem\Nfor any motoring enthusiast.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.52,1:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可那跟这个赛道有什么关系\NSo, what's it got to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.24,1:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得找到比赛的状态才行\NWe've got to get match fit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.08,1:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样等我们明天到了波城\NAnd then when we get to Pau tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.68,1:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们就能值回票钱 -没错\N- We'll be worthy of it.\N- Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.12,1:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一上赛道 我顿时就开心了起来\NStraightaway,I was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.32,1:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有湿乎乎的赛道 没有泥巴\NNo wet track, no mud,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.20,1:16:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有下不停的雨 也没有得白喉的可能\Nno rain, no diphtheria.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.52,1:17:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是一条紧凑蜿蜒的赛道\NThis is one\Ntight and twisty little track.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.80,1:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 下面我们就让这辆阿斯顿\NRight, now, let's turn the Aston
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.48,1:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,从公路车变的更赛道化一点\Nfrom a road car into something\Nmore track-based.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.60,1:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,按下这个让悬挂变得更硬的按钮\NWe'll push this button here,\Nthat firms up the suspension.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.60,1:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再按这个S按钮 我猜它的意思是 傻缺模式\Nand then push this one, S,\NI think it stands for "silly".
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.32,1:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当你按下它的时候 准备好了吗\N'Cause when you push it... Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.84,1:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,整辆车好似瞬间变身 "嗯 要干嘛？"\N好比向狗狗下达"朝前走" 的命令一样\NThe whole car goes, "Hmm, what?"\NIt's like saying "walkies" to a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.84,1:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"真的 主人？ 向前走？"\N"Oh, really? WaIkies?"
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.80,1:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这辆车所用的引擎跟老版Vanquish一样\NThis has the same basic engine that\Nwas fitted to the original Vanquish.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.92,1:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这在当时是能够比肩法拉利550的引擎\NAnd that was comparable\Nat the time to the Ferrari 550
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.52,1:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是575\Nor 575.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.28,1:17:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但从那以后 法拉利继续发展\N人家都生产出F12那样的车了\NSince then, Ferrari have moved on,\Nthey're at the F12 now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.32,1:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这车的变速器甚至都不是双离合\NThis doesn't even have\Na double-clutch gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.88,1:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而是老式的七速顺序变速器\NIt's an old 7-speed slushmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.12,1:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,每次换挡都像是一个年长的男仆完成的\NEach gear is delivered\Nby an elderly butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.36,1:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我想换三档了 吉夫斯 -没问题先生\N"I'd like third now, Jeeves."\N"Certainly, sir, I'll just
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.36,1:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)}Jeeves 小说中人物 常指理想的男仆
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.48,1:18:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就去拿 应该放在餐具室了\N"pop off and get it.\NI think it's in my pantry.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.76,1:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给您拿来了 先生\N"There you are, sir."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.60,1:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,换挡非常顺畅 应付公路绰绰有余\N但在赛道上就不合适了\NVery smooth,\Nlovely on the road, not brilliant here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.36,1:18:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这车开起来有点像方舟\NIt's a bit of an ark, this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.92,1:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是非常 非常漂亮的方舟\NIt's a very pretty ark.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.96,1:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不过每当在赛道上攻入一个弯的时候\NBut when you stick it into\Na corner on a track...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.00,1:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你能够感觉到在这副碳纤维的身躯下\Nyou know that beneath\Nthe carbon fibre body,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.76,1:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每个零件都感觉有点年事已高\Neverything's a bit old.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.92,1:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过如你所见 倒不是说老就一定不好\NNot that theres much\Nwrong with old, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.68,1:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时 在落后我很多的地方\NMean while, far behind...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.80,1:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德在新911强大的抓地力下撒着欢儿\NHammond was\Nrevelling in the new 917's grip.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.52,1:19:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 这玩意就和长在地上似的\NGod, this thing is planted.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.12,1:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,依旧是3.8升的水平对置六缸引擎\NStill a 3.8-litre flat six,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.12,1:19:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,依旧位居车尾 依然那么紧凑\Nit's still mounted at the back\Nof the car, it's still compact.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.80,1:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不过最大的问题 还是电子转向\NThe big issue, though,\Nis that electric steering.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.24,1:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它根本没有向我沟通 没有\N它本应该反馈给我各种信息\NIt's not talking to me. It's not...\NIt should be telling me everything
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.76,1:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,比如加速过弯的时候前面切弯稍浅\Nby going slightly\Nlight at the front under power.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.60,1:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着前轮比于普通的车\NIt means the front wheels can move\Naround a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.80,1:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再多打一点方向\Nthan they would in an ordinary car.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.28,1:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而方向盘本应该告诉我这一切\NAnd the steering wheel\Nshould be telling me about that,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.68,1:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这才能让我知道它是911\Nthat's what lets me know it is a 911
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.16,1:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是R8或者捷豹什么的\Nand not an R8 or a Jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.36,1:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要问我这车有没有那种911韵味\NDoes it feel like a 911?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.80,1:20:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我还真不觉得有\NI don't think it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.52,1:20:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要是为波城选战车的话\N我想要比它跟纯一点的\NAnd for Pau, I want something\Nthat's more of a 911.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.64,1:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而我已经有了个很好的想法\NAnd I've had a very good idea for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.16,1:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该用这车\NI shall be using this,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.60,1:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,全新的保时捷911GT3\Nthe brand-new Porsche 991 GT3.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.00,1:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我太想开这车了\NI am desperate to drive it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.08,1:20:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,更轻 更强 更快\NIt's lighter, lower, faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.24,1:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它就是我的独角兽\NThis is my unicorn,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.08,1:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的女神\Nmy Helena.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.16,1:20:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,GT3或许在赛道方面更专业\NTrack-focused the GT3 may be,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.12,1:20:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在波城 它跟我的选择根本没得比\Nbut at Pau, it would be no\Nmatch for my choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.20,1:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,单座的BAC Mono\NThe single-seater BACMono.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.96,1:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们测试赛道上有史以来最快的车之一\NOne of the fastest cars ever\Nto take on the Top Gear test track.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.36,1:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,极致的简洁 轻盈 灵动 平衡\NPurity simplified,\Nlight, agile, balanced.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.00,1:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,完美\NPerfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.88,1:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当工作人员正为明天的大日子准备车子时\NAs men set about fettling our cars\Nfor the big day...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.48,1:21:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩回顾了在这段旅程中我们所驾驶的\Nwe ruminated on all the boats\Nand bikes and cars
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.28,1:21:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所有摩托车 汽车 船\Nthat we 'd used on our journey.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.32,1:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德!\N- Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.04,1:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,试图找出我们最喜欢的那一个\NAnd we tried to work out\Nwhich one we 'd liked the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.96,1:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我大爱那辆小嘉年华ST 真心的\NI loved that little Fiesta ST,\NI really did.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.44,1:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然听着很疯狂 但那辆福特T型我也喜欢\NI actually loved driving the Model-T,\Ncrazy though that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.92,1:21:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杜卡迪也令人十分享受\NI enjoyed the Ducati.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.92,1:21:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不知为何 法拉利F12确实让我倾心\NBut for some reason, the Ferrari F12\Nhas really stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.20,1:22:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得它有那种韵味和戏剧性\N更不用说它的速度!\NI thought it had presence and drama\Nand it's fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.80,1:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会选SLS 因为日常开着有点过了\NI wouldn't have the SLS 'cause\Nthat's too much to use every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.96,1:22:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,高尔夫GTI会有点不够用\NGolf GTI isn't quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.44,1:22:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,布加迪威龙的话就完全不是一个级别了\NBugatti Veyron, I mean it's\Nthe other end of the scale, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.00,1:22:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也太过了 宾利的话\NToo much. Bentley...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.76,1:22:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是辆好车但是...\N我知道究竟喜欢哪个了\NOh, it's a great car but...\NI've worked out what I'd have.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.20,1:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Riva Aquarama那条船\NThe Riva Aquarama.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.00,1:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是你最喜欢的 车 -是的\N- That's your favourite car?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.36,1:22:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是让我天天用 我会选那个\N不过那样我就得搬家喽\NThat's what I'd use every day.\NI'd have to move house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.08,1:22:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,选出我们最喜欢的那辆\N我们重新坐上了自己的公路车\NWith that decided,\Nwe climbed back into our road cars
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.24,1:22:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,驶上前往波城的最后一段路\Nfor the final push to Pau.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.52,1:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,即将到达波城 我俩十分激动\NWe were very excited by what lay ahead,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.16,1:22:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太激动了 以至于我们把摄制组落了很远\Nso excited that we left\Nthe camera crew far behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.36,1:22:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当他们终于追上的时候 却出了点小状况\NAnd when they finally caught up with us,\Nthere was a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.64,1:22:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,护照是吧\NYou mean, passports?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.16,1:23:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对 坏了\NOh, right
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.88,1:23:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,法国的警察和女警们\NThe French policemen and lady policemen
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.48,1:23:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持要我们交出所有的钱\Ninsisted that we should give\Nthem all our money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.84,1:23:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而在一段长谈之后\NAnd then after quite a long chat,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.08,1:23:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不允许我们在法国境内再开车了\Nthey decided it would be best\Nif we didn't drive in France any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.56,1:23:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好 没问题\NYeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.72,1:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那么伴随着这个爆炸性新闻 我们该结束了\NAnd on that bombshell,\Nit is time to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.28,1:23:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢各位的收看 再见\NThank you very much for watching,\Ngoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.12,1:23:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你个纯种的笨蛋\NYou total plonker!
